%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Refuses%20to%20Allow%20Widowed%20Woman%20to%20Terminate%2032-Week%20Pregnancy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20(February%201)%20refused%20to%20allow%20a%20widowed%20woman%20who%20is%2032%20weeks%20pregnant%20to%20undergo%20an%20abortion.%20The%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20medical%20board%20had%20opined%20against%20the%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%2C%20and%20the%20bench%20suggested%20that%20the%20woman%20could%20put%20the%20baby%20up%20for%20adoption%20once%20it%20is%20born%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-rejects-widows-plea-to-abort-32-week-pregnancy-suggests-giving-child-for-adoption-248150%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELivelaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20abnormality%20in%20the%20foetus.%20It%20is%20a%20full-fledged%2C%20normal-bodied%20child.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20case%20we%20should%20entertain%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20bench%20headed%20by%20Justice%20Bela%20M.%20Trivedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20just%20a%20question%20of%20another%20two%20weeks%20or%20so.%20Even%20the%20government%20is%20willing%20to%20take%20the%20child%20for%20adoption.%20The%20medical%20board%20says%20her%20life%20will%20be%20at%20risk%20in%20a%20pre-term%20pregnancy.%20We%20cannot%20permit%20it.%20All%20these%20points%20have%20been%20considered%20by%20the%20high%20court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20petition%2C%20the%2026-year-old%20woman%20had%20argued%20that%20the%20pregnancy%20was%20causing%20her%20mental%20trauma%20and%20depression.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20a%20widow%20and%20she%20does%20not%20want%20to%20live%20with%20this%20trauma.%20This%20pregnancy%20is%20against%20her%20ch