st-harsh-mander%5C%22%3Espoken%20out%20strongly%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20these%20raids%2C%20terming%20them%20%E2%80%9Charassment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20invoked%20Section%203%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act%20(FCRA)%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffcra-harsh-mander-think-tank-ces-suspended-columnist%5C%22%3Esuspend%20CES%E2%80%99s%20FCRA%20license%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20section%20bars%20any%20%E2%80%9Ccorrespondent%2C%20columnist%2C%20cartoonist%2C%20editor%2C%20owner%2C%20printer%20or%20publisher%20of%20a%20registered%20newspaper%E2%80%9D%20from%20accepting%20any%20foreign%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMander%2C%20a%20former%20IAS%20officer%2C%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20campaign%20against%20communal%20disharmony%20in%20India%20and%20has%20been%20severely%20critical%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20for%20allegedly%20fuelling%20majoritarian%20politics%20in%20the%20country.%20His%20NGO%E2%80%99s%20research%20work%20has%20also%20highlighted%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failings%20in%20insuring%20an%20equitable%2C%20safe%20India%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECentral%20agencies%20have%20been%20under%20fire%20for%20focused%20attention%20on%20those%20who%20coincidentally%20are%20government%20critics%2C%20in%20the%20opposition%20or%20not%20aligned%20with%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20project.%20In%20a%20discussion%20with%20ex-chief%20minister%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%2C%20senior%20advocate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWCp__8kETUY%3Fsi%3DQv-HJpYkwL_IidrR%5C%22%3EKapil%20Sibal%20pointed%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20without%20FIRs%2C%20those%20seen%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20political%20divide%20are%20under%20the%20lens%2C%20whereas%20over%2030%20Central%20ministers%20(with%20criminal%20cases%2C%20declared%20in%20their%20election%20affidavits)%20are%20off%20the