0Institute%20of%20Population%20Studies%20(IIPS)%20in%20Mumbai%20organised%20themselves%20to%20celebrate%20the%20consecration%20of%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20campus%2C%20many%20Bahujan%20students%20feared%20the%20frenzy%20could%20cause%20communal%20tension.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20a%20letter%20seeking%20the%20institute%E2%80%99s%20immediate%20intervention%20in%20restoring%20peace%20on%20campus%20was%20submitted%20to%20IIPS%20direct%20S.K.%20Singh.%20The%20letter%2C%20submitted%20on%20January%2020%2C%20was%20confidential%20and%20around%2035%20students%20had%20signed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20failed%20to%20intervene.%20And%20worse%20still%2C%20the%20names%20of%20students%20who%20had%20signed%20the%20letter%20was%20made%20public.%20One%20masters%20student%2C%20who%20was%20instrumental%20in%20getting%20students%20together%20to%20sign%20the%20protest%20letter%2C%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2023-year-old%20student%20belonging%20to%20a%20Dalit%20community%20from%20Latur%20district%20was%20arrested%20on%20January%2022.%20He%20was%20arrested%20after%20a%20senior%20student%20filed%20an%20FIR%20against%20him%20for%20putting%20out%20a%20status%20on%20WhatsApp%20against%20the%20frenzy%20created%20all%20around%20on%20the%20consecration%20day.%20In%20the%20post%2C%20the%20student%20took%20a%20critical%20take%20against%20the%20celebration.%20It%20was%20a%20copied%20post%20from%20another%20fellow%20student.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20students%20had%20put%20out%20social%20media%20statuses%20in%20protest%20of%20the%20ongoing%20celebrations%20on%20the%20IIPS%20campus.%20But%20only%20one%20student%20was%20singled%20out%20and%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20students%20that%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20say%20that%20the%20post%20was%20a%20mere%20excuse.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20said%20student%20would%20have%20become%20a%20target%20anyway.%20Many%20students%20and%20even%20the%20administration%20were%20not%20happy%20with%20the%20student%20and%20his%20friends%E2%80%99%20endeavour%20of%20organising%20students%20against%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20celebration%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20the%20students%2C%20who%20too%20had%20signed%20the%20letter%20sent%20to%20the%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20students%20wrote%3A%20%E2%80%9CIIPS%20is%20a%20multicultural%20campus%20annually%20organising%20various%20celebrations%20which%20includes%20Ganesh%20Chaturthi%2C%20Dussehra%2C%20Christmas%2C%20etc%20which%20epitomises%20the%20promise%20of%20grooming%20a%20secular%20young%20generation%20who%20can%20contribute%20prosperity%20to%20a%20diversified%20nation-state%20like%20India.%20But%20the%20celebration%20of%20Ram%20temple%20consecration%20is%20a%20pure%20act%20of%20political%20agenda%20orchestrated%20by%20the%20various%20outfits%2C%20which%20can%20harm%20the%20secular%20sentiments%20of%20students%20while%20celebrating%20in%20an%20institute%20like%20IIPS%2C%20where%20such%20celebrations%20cannot%20be%20done.%E2%80%9D%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20students%20sought%20restrictions%20on%20celebrations%20on%20campus%20and%20said%20the%20celebration%20had%20the%20potential%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfurther%20deepening%20the%20divisions%20among%20student%20fraternity%20by%20spreading%20hate%20and%20fear%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20was%20overlooked.%20But%20after%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20those%20who%20had%20submitted%20the%20letter%20were%20bullied%20into%20writing%20an%20apology.%20Contrary%20to%20the%20concerns%20raised%20in%20the%20earlier%20letter%2C%20the%20students%20this%20time%20were%20made%20to%20apologise%20for%20hurting%20sentiments%20of%20those%20celebrating%20the%20Ram%20temple%20consecration.%20Both%20the%20letters%20were%20addressed%20to%20the%20director.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20555px)%2085vw%2C%20555px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F020