alked%20of%20benefiting%20the%20four%20%E2%80%98castes%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20poor%2C%20farmers%2C%20women%20and%20the%20youth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman%20has%20followed%20through%20on%20the%20president%E2%80%99s%20address%20to%20the%20parliament%2C%20which%20listed%20the%20many%20achievements%20of%20the%20government%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20But%20one%20thought%20that%20the%20budget%2C%20following%20the%20exhortation%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20would%20move%20towards%20establishment%20of%20Ram%20Rajya.%20So%2C%20it%20would%20chart%20a%20different%20path.%20It%20would%20present%20an%20honest%20picture%20of%20the%20economy%20and%20take%20steps%20to%20address%20the%20issues%20of%20poverty%20and%20uncivilised%20conditions%20of%20living%20of%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20citizens.%20Without%20these%20steps%20there%20can%20be%20no%20Ram%20Rajya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20should%20the%20budget%20have%20contained%3F%20Big%20increase%20in%20allocations%20for%20employment%20and%20agriculture.%20That%20is%20what%20is%20needed%20by%20the%20youth%2C%20women%20and%20the%20farmers.%20It%20would%20have%20also%20mitigated%20poverty.%20The%20finance%20minister%20while%20announcing%20many%20things%20in%20the%20budget%20should%20have%20announced%20that%20henceforth%20workers%20will%20get%20a%20%E2%80%98living%20wage%E2%80%99%20promised%20in%20the%20Constitution.%20For%20the%20farmers%2C%20the%20announcement%20should%20have%20been%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20promised%20full%20cost%20price%20MSP%20for%20all%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22As%20Corporates%20Hijack%20Union%20Budget%2C%20Agriculture%20Is%20No%20Longer%20a%20Priority%20of%20the%20Modi%20Government%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-interim-budget-agriculture-fuel%5C%22%3EAs%20Corporates%20Hijack%20Union%20Budget%2C%20Agriculture%20Is%20No%20Longer%20a%20Priority%20of%20the%20Modi%20Government%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20these%20critical%20steps%20were%20announced.%20Instead%2C%20vague%20promises%20have%20been%20made%20which%20cannot%20be%20achieved%20with%20the%20presently%20structured%20economy%20and%20the%20budget.%20Unemployment%20and%20poverty%20would%20persist%20so%20that%20the%20lot%20of%20the%20young%20and%20women%20is%20unlikely%20to%20improve.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20effect%2C%20the%20budget%20will%20not%20initiate%20the%20Ram%20Rajya%20promised%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20just%20a%20week%20back.%20The%20first%20thing%20to%20do%20to%20move%20towards%20Ram%20Rajya%20is%20to%20be%20honest%20about%20data%20and%20one%E2%80%99s%20intentions.%20Neither%20of%20these%20are%20evident%20in%20the%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20macro%20aspects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20India%20is%20to%20become%20a%20%2430-trillion%20economy%20in%20real%20terms%20by%202030%2C%20a%20real%20growth%20rate%20of%209.55%25%20is%20required.%20Currently%20the%20average%20growth%20rate%20over%20the%20last%2010%20years%20has%20been%20about%206%25.%20If%20this%20persists%2C%20India%20will%20only%20reach%20%2414.1%20trillion.%20The%20per%20capita%20income%20would%20also%20be%20only%20%249000%2C%20not%20the%20required%20%2414%2C000%20at%20which%20income%20a%20country%20is%20considered%20to%20be%20rich.%20So%2C%20why%20promise%20what%20is%20unlikely%3F%20It%20can%20only%20be%20for%20effect%20to%20get%20votes.%20That%20is%20not%20what%20maryada%20of%20the%20rulers%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20boost%20the%20economy%E2%80%99s%20average%20growth%20rate%2C%20there%20is%20need%20to%20tackle%20the%20macro%20constraints%20of%20the%20economy.%20The%20biggest%20constraint%20for%20a%20while%20has%20been%20the%20lack%20of%20adequate%20demand%20due%20to%20rising%20inequality%20and%20lack%20of%20purchasing%20power%20of%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20Indians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20budget%20could%20have%20been%20used%20to%20boost%20overall%20demand%20and%20also%20make%20it%20possible%20for%20the%20poor%20to%20have%20higher%20incomes%20through%20robust%20employment%20generation.%20On%20both%20these%20fronts%20the%20budget%20is%20lacking.%20Compared%20to%20last%20year%2C%20the%20overall%20expenditure%20is%20going%20to%20rise%20by%20only%206.1%25%20which%20is%20barely%20above%20the%20rate%20of%20inflation%2C%20so%20that%20not%20much%20of%20a%20boost%20is%20going%20to%20come%20from%20this%20factor.%20The%20increase%20in%20expenditure%20should%20have%20been%20substantial.%20The%20primary%20deficit%20is%20also%20being%20sharply%20reduced%20from%202.3%25%20to%201.5%25.%20This%20will%20also%20reduce%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20employment%2C%20capital%20intensive%20areas%20are%20being%20promoted%20not%20labour%20intensive%20ones.%20Even%20modern%20construction%20is%20highly%20capital%20intensive.%20What%20was%20needed%20was%20to%20boost%20MGNREGA%2C%20education%2C%20health%20and%20rural%20development%20spending%2C%20which%20are%20all%20big%20employers.%20No%20scheme%20for%20urban%20employment%20generation%20has%20been%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESectoral%20aspects%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allocation%20in%20the%20last%20year%E2%80%99s%20budget%20for%20agriculture%20was%20Rs.1.44%20lakh%20crore%20but%20what%20is%20spent%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20Rs.1.4%20lakh%20crore.%20For%20the%20next%20year%20it%20is%20Rs.1.47%20lakh%20crore%20which%20is%20barely%201.5%25%20above%20the%20allocation%20currently.%20This%20will%20not%20even%20cover%20inflation%20so%20in%20real%20terms%20it%20will%20be%20less.%20So%2C%20even%20the%20inadequate%20allocation%20is%20not%20spent%2C%20so%20how%20can%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20incomes%20improve%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20poor%20need%20education%20and%20health%20to%20upgrade%20themselves%20to%20be%20able%20to%20get%20better%20jobs%2Fwork.%20For%20education%20the%20allocation%20last%20year%20was%20Rs%201.16%20lakh%20crore%20which%20was%20reduced%20to%20Rs%201.09%20lakh%20crore%20and%20for%20next%20year%20it%20is%20slated%20to%20get%20Rs%201.25%20lakh%20crore.%20For%20health%20the%20allocation%20last%20year%20was%20Rs%2089%2C000%20crore%20but%20what%20is%20spent%20is%20Rs%2079%2C000%20crore.%20For%20next%20year%2C%20the%20allocation%20is%20Rs%2090%2C000%20thousand%20crore.%20Not%20only%20are%20these%20inadequate%20compared%20to%20what%20is%20needed%20but%20even%20these%20allocations%20are%20not%20spent.%20One%20would%20have%20expected%20a%20quantum%20jump%20in%20the%20allocations%20to%20these%20sectors%20but%20this%20is%20not%20in%20evidence%20and%20even%20if%20allocations%20are%20made%20they%20are%20not%20fulfilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Budget%202024%3A%20How%20the%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Neglected%20Social%20Security%20Pensions%20Once%20Again%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbudget-2024-how-the-modi-government-has-neglected-social-security-pensions-once-again%5C%22%3EBudget%202024%3A%20How%20the%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Neglected%20Social%20Security%20Pensions%20Once%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECorruption%20and%20black%20economy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20finance%20minister%20has%20promised%20better%20governance%20which%20is%20so%20crucial%20for%20proper%20implementation%20and%20better%20outcomes%20from%20the%20schemes%20announced.%20In%20this%20regard%2C%20Transparency%20International%20has%20just%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fglobal-corruption-index-2023-india-ranks-93rd-out-of-180-countries-was-85th-in-2022%5C%22%3Ereleased%20its%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pointing%20to%20India%20slipping%20in%20the%20rankings.%20Thus%2C%20better%20compliance%20is%20not%20in%20sight.%20That%20is%20why%20in%20India%20big%20announcements%20do%20not%20lead%20to%20big%20outcomes%20and%2For%20improvements%20in%20the%20lot%20of%20the%20common%20persons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20a%20big%20scheme%20has%20been%20announced%20for%20installation%20of%20rooftop%20solar%20panels.%20Such%20a%20scheme%20has%20been%20ongoing%20for%20some%20time.%20Talking%20to%20those%20who%20install%20these%20devices%2C%20it%20becomes%20clear%20that%20the%20scheme%20is%20mired%20in%20corruption%20and%20non-implementation.%20So%2C%20how%20to%20get%20good%20intentions%20to%20fructify.%20The%20black%20economy%20has%20to%20be%20brought%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20black%20economy%20had%20been%20checked%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20as%20often%20claimed%2C%20direct%20tax%20to%20GDP%20ratio%20would%20have%20sharply%20risen.%20It%20has%20barely%20risen%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20to%206.1%25%20from%205.7%25.%20So%2C%20the%20black%20economy%20is%20not%20being%20dented%20by%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20the%20government.%20No%20wonder%20there%20are%20daily%20reports%20of%20new%20cases%20of%20corruption.%20If%20the%20black%20economy%20could%20have%20been%20controlled%2C%20there%20would%20be%20more%20resources%20for%20development%20and%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20would%20be%20eliminated.%20The%20economy%20would%20have%20become%20more%20efficient%20and%20growth%20rate%20would%20have%20risen%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConclusion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20optics%20of%20the%20budget%20presented%20is%20an%20election%20budget%20with%20big%20claims%20and%20promises%20on%20which%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20going%20to%20campaign.%20Neither%20its%20macroeconomics%20nor%20the%20sectoral%20allocations%20are%20such%20as%20to%20help%20either%20the%20poor%20or%20the%20economy%20to%20achieve%20new%20heights.%20Is%20this%20not%20a%20slap%20on%20the%20face%20of%20the%20citizens%20who%20have%20been%20promised%20Ram%20Rajya%2C%20which%20stands%20for%20justice%20and%20honesty%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EArun%20Kumar%20retired%20as%20professor%20of%20economics%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%20He%20is%20the%20author%20of%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EUnderstanding%20Black%20Economy%20and%20Black%20Money%20in%20India%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706842917000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22170222%2FEffect-78.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funion-budget-2024-has-elections-and-not-ram-rajya-in-sight%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neither%20its%20macroeconomics%20nor%20the%20sectoral%20allocations%20are%20such%20as%20to%20help%20either%20the%20poor%20or%20the%20economy%20to%20achieve%20new%20heights%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funion-budget-2024-has-elections-and-not-ram-rajya-in-sight%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Justin%20TROLLED%20for%20shading%20Britney%20-%20Watch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706842808000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107339389%2Cimgsize-43988.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fjustin-timberlake-shades-britney-spears-in-latest-video-singer-claps-back%2Farticleshow%2F107339379.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107339379.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJustin%20Timberlake%20sparks%20controversy%20with%20comments%20believed%20to%20be%20directed%20at%20Britney%20Spears%20during%20a%20concert.%20Britney%20recently%20apologized%20for%20her%20memoir%2C%20while%20also%20expressing%20her%20admiration%20for%20Justin's%20new%20song.%20Fans%20criticize%20Justin%20for%20his%20immature%20behavior%2C%20with%20some%20accusing%20him%20of%20misogyny.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ft