2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-president-biden-sanctions-4-israeli-settlers-over-west-bank-violence%2Farticleshow%2F107339393.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107339393.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-president-biden-sanctions-4-israeli-settlers-over-west-bank-violence%2Farticleshow%2F107339393.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-president-biden-sanctions-4-israeli-settlers-over-west-bank-violence%2Famp_articleshow%2F107339393.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-president-biden-sanctions-4-israeli-settlers-over-west-bank-violence%2Famp_articleshow%2F107339393.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Corporates%20Hijack%20Union%20Budget%2C%20Agriculture%20Is%20No%20Longer%20a%20Priority%20of%20the%20Modi%20Government%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24161455%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-4.14.04.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20plays%20an%20important%20role%20in%20designing%20the%20investment%20priority%20of%20the%20state%20governments%20towards%20agriculture.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%20budgetary%20contribution%20allows%20the%20country%20to%20maintain%20growth%20parity%20across%20the%20regions%2C%20check%20regional%20imbalances%20through%20resource%20support%20to%20states%2C%20give%20policy%20support%2C%20research%20and%20experimental%20development%20support%2C%20address%20social%20inequities%2C%20design%C2%A0%20innovation%20ecosystems%2C%20boost%20trade%2C%20facilitate%20private%20investment%20in%20food%20processing%20and%20agro%20processing%2C%20ensure%20food%20security%2C%20contribute%20to%20agro-ecosystem%20health%2C%20help%20with%20the%20conservation%20of%20forests%2C%20rivers%2C%20ground%20water%2C%20animals%2C%20and%20fisheries%2C%20and%20promote%20systematic%20utilisation%20of%20lands%20available%20for%20agriculture%20and%20rural%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20three%20major%20central%20sector%20schemes%2C%20which%20form%20nearly%2080%25-85%25%20of%20the%20budget%20of%20the%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Welfare%20(DA%26amp%3BFW)%20allocations%20for%20agriculture%20of%20the%20last%20four%20years.%20We%20have%20seen%20high%20priority%20for%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Kisan%20Samman%20Nidhi%20Yojana%20(PM-KISAN)%20and%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Fasal%20Bima%20Yojana%20(PMFBY).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPM-KISAN%20was%20launched%20in%202019%20and%20offers%20direct%20income%20support%20of%20merely%20Rs%206%2C000%20on%20an%20annual%20basis.%20It%20is%20not%20a%20cultivator-centric%20scheme.%20It%20gives%20support%20to%20the%20landowner.%20Close%20to%2040%25%20of%20the%20cultivators%20today%20are%20tenant%20farmers%20and%20do%20not%20get%20the%20benefit%20of%20this%20scheme.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClose%20to%20half%20of%20the%20DA%26amp%3BFW%20budget%20amounting%20to%20Rs.%2060%2C000%20crores%20has%20been%20allocated%20to%20PM-KISAN.%20The%20PMFBY%20has%20been%20allocated%20Rs%2014%2C600%20crores.%20The%20main%20beneficiary%20of%20PMFBY%20is%20private%20insurance.%20Farmers%20are%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnavigating-pm-kisan-a-deep-dive-into-digital-challenges-faced-by-farmers%5C%22%3ENavigating%20PM-KISAN%3A%20A%20Deep%20Dive%20into%20Digital%20Challenges%20Faced%20by%20Farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20modified%20interest%20subvention%20scheme%20(MISS)%20is%20allocated%20Rs%2022%2C600%20crores.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESector-wide%20support%20measures%20have%20been%20witnessing%20decreased%20allocations%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%20There%20is%20a%20further%20decrease%20in%20the%20allocation%20for%20sector-wide%20measures.%20The%20emerging%20pattern%20of%20declining%20share%20of%20allocation%20for%20measures%20required%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20longer-term%20and%20sustained%20improvements%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20high%20concern.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECentral%20schemes%20which%20include%20Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(RKVY)%20and%20Krishionnati%20Yojana%20have%20received%20this%20year%20merely%2013%25%20of%20the%20total%20allocation%20made%20by%20DA%26amp%3BFW.%20The%20challenge%20of%20implementation%20of%20sector-wide%20support%20measures%20at%20the%20state%20level%20is%20on%20the%20rise%20because%20the%20fiscally%20challenged%20state%20governments%20have%20to%20bear%20a%20greater%20burden%20for%20fund%20utilisation%20in%20the%20case%20of%20sector-wide%20support%20measures.%20In%20several%20states%2C%20the%20extent%20of%20utilisation%20against%20allocation%20under%20two%20of%20the%20important%20sector-wide%20schemes%20%E2%80%93%20RKVY%20and%20National%20Food%20Security%20Mission%20(NFSM)%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20low.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImproving%20the%20extent%20and%20quality%20of%20fund%20utilisation%20in%20the%20sector%20of%20agriculture%20requires%20strengthening%20of%20institutions%20and%20enhancing%20frontline%20staff.%20But%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20transferring%20the%20control%20of%20public%20assets%20created%20for%20agricultural%20education%2C%20research%20and%20extension%2C%20production%20and%20distribution%20of%20agricultural%20inputs%2C%20agricultural%20credit%2C%20electricity%20generation%2C%20transmission%20and%20distribution%2C%20digitalisation%20of%20agriculture%2C%20procurement%2C%20agro%20processing%2C%20food%20processing%20and%20value%20addition%20to%20the%20corporate%20sector.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20share%20of%20investment%20in%20agriculture%20for%20public%20capital%20formation%20has%20steadily%20gone%20down%20over%20the%20last%2050%20years%3B%20now%20an%20overwhelming%20share%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eagricultural%20investments%20is%20of%20the%20private%20household%20sector%20at%2082%25.%20Investment%20by%20public%20sector%20is%20at%2015%25.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20remaining%20share%20of%20investment%20at%203%25%20is%20by%20the%20private%20corporate%20sector%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20had%20earlier%20a%20number%20of%20sector-wide%20development%20programmes%20from%20the%20Union%20government%20side%20to%20arrest%20the%20ecosystem%20health%2C%20in%20particular%20land%20degradation.%20Integrated%20Watershed%20Management%20Programme%2C%20National%20Afforestation%20programme%20(NAP)%2C%20National%20Mission%20for%20Green%20India%20(GIM)%2C%20Soil%20Conservation%20in%20the%20Catchment%20of%20River%20Valley%20Project%2C%20National%20Watershed%20Development%20Project%20for%20Rain-fed%20areas%2C%20Fodder%20and%20Feed%20Development%20Scheme%20as%20a%20component%20of%20Grassland%20Development%2C%20Command%20Area%20Development%20and%20Water%20Management%20Programme%2C%20and%20many%20other%20such%20programmes%20used%20to%20receive%20greater%20share%20of%20allocations.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20share%20has%20been%20further%20reduced%20in%20the%20budget%20allocations%20of%202024-25.%20Agricultural%20intensification-centric%20programmes%20will%20have%20to%20depend%20on%20external%20inputs%20supplied%20by%20the%20corporate%20sector.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbudget-2024-how-the-modi-government-has-neglected-social-security-pensions-once-again%5C%22%3EBudget%202024%3A%20How%20the%20Modi%20Government%20Has%20Neglected%20Social%20Security%20Pensions%20Once%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20last%20four%20years%2C%20Union%20government%20budgets%20have%20tended%20to%20promote%20interventions%20in%20linked%20sectors%20(animal%20husbandry%2C%20biomass%20utilisation%2C%20forestry%20and%20so%20on)%20mainly%20through%20the%20corporate%20sector.%20Corporate%20sector%20programmes%20are%20not%20aligned%20to%20land%20degradation%20prevention%20priority.%20They%20do%20not%20focus%20on%20priority%20on%20the%20challenge%20of%20soil%20fertility%20enhancement.%20Corporates%20do%20not%20care%20for%20the%20earth%20or%20farmers.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20in%20the%20budget%20of%202024-25%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20Union%20government%20is%20on%20the%20promotion%20of%20%E2%80%98SATAT%E2%80%99%20scheme%20and%20%E2%80%98SAMARTH%E2%80%99%20scheme.%20SATAT%20is%20focused%20on%20Compressed%20Bio%20Gas%20(CBG)%2C%20a%20scheme%20that%20encourages%20entrepreneurs%20to%20set%20up%20CBG%20plants%2C%20produce%20and%20supply%20CBG%20to%20oil-marketing%20companies%20(OMCs)%20for%20sale%20as%20automotive%20and%20industrial%20fuels.%20SAMARTH%20is%20a%20Sustainable%20Agrarian%20Mission%20that%20promotes%20the%20use%20of%20Agri-Residue%20in%20Thermal%20power%20plants.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20support%20for%20bio-energy%20programme%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20New%20and%20Renewable%20Energy%20(MNRE)%20has%20been%20raised%20by%20four%20times.%20The%20programmes%20announced%20under%20the%20rubric%20of%20bio-energy%2C%20bio%20manufacturing%2C%20bio-refineries%20are%20closely%20linked%20to%20the%20promotion%20of%20compressed%20biogas%20and%20ethanol%20production.%20The%20Union%20government%20is%20promoting%20GOBAR-Dhan%20Scheme%20(Galvanising%20Organic%20Bio-Agro%20Resources)%20through%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Jalshakti.%20The%20goals%20of%20this%20scheme%20are%20suspect%20now.%20The%202018%20scheme%20started%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20keeping%20villages%20clean%2C%20increasing%20the%20income%20of%20rural%20households%20and%20generating%20energy%20from%20cattle%20waste.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20GOBAR-DHAN%20scheme%20is%20also%20linked%20to%20the%20programme%20of%20promoting%20mandatory%20use%20of%20bio-fuels%20and%20is%20being%20coordinated%20through%20a%20unified%20registration%20portal%20for%20biogas%2C%20CBG%20and%20bio-CNG%20plants.%20The%20vision%20is%20to%20run%20cars%20in%20AmritKaal%20in%20India%20with%20bio-fuels.%20The%20claim%20that%20the%20current%20government%20wishes%20to%20make%20the%20farmers%20not%20just%20%3Cem%3Eannadata%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20givers%20of%20rice%20%E2%80%93%20but%20%3Cem%3Eurjadata%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20givers%20of%20strength%20%E2%80%93%20is%20a%20misleading%20assertion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Union%20government-funded%20programmes%20are%20encouraging%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20use%20of%20bio-resources%20to%20a%20bio-economy%20focused%20on%20fuel%20supply%20rather%20than%20food%20supply.%20All%20biogas%20plants%20require%20a%20large%20investment.%20Credit%20systems%20and%20public%20finance%20are%20promoting%20NBFCs%20embedded%20in%20agribusiness%20to%20undertake%20co-lending%20to%20sell%20agricultural%20inputs%20under%20production%20in%20the%20corporate%20sector.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20reality%2C%20the%20programmes%20under%20promotion%20are%20not%20for%20actual%20farmers.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0Dinesh%20Abrol%20retired%20as%20Chief%20Scientist%20CSIR-NISTADS%2C%20and%20was%20also%20professor%20at%20ISID.%20He%20is%20currently%20faculty%20at%20TRCSS%2C%20JNU.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706840448000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F24161455%2FScreenshot-2023-11-24-at-4.14.04.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-interim-budget-agriculture-fuel%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20government-funded%20programmes%20are%20encouraging%20a%20shift%20in%20the%20use%20of%20bio-resources%20to%20a%20bio-economy%20focused%20on%20fuel%20supply%20rather%20than%20food%20supply.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-interim-budget-agriculture-fuel%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20launches%20Rufus%2C%20its%20new%20AI-powered%20assistant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706840327000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107339320%2Cimgsize-634835.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Famazon-rufus-aipowered-assistant-for-online-shoppers-launch%2Farticleshow%2F107339327.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amazon%20launches%20Rufus%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20assistant%20for%20online%20shoppers.%20Rufus%20is%20trained%20on%20Amazon's%20product%20catalog%20and%20web%20information%20to%20answer%20customer%20questions%2C%20make%20recommendations%2C%20and%20facilitate%20product%20discovery.%20It%20is%20currently%20available%20in%20beta%20on%20Amazon's%20mobile%20app%20in%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Famazon-rufus-aipowered-assistant-for-online-shoppers-launch%2Farticleshow%2F107339327.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Iran's%20Guards%20pull%20officers%20from%20Syria%20after%20Israeli%20strikes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706839969000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107339371%2Cimgsize-1421516.cms%22%2C%22o