r.%20Local%20ski%20mountains%20were%20our%20backyard%2C%20so%20hitting%20the%20nearby%20slopes%20every%20winter%20was%20easy.%20Even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-whistler-canada-popular-ski-destinations-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhistler%20Blackcomb%20ski%20resort%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20only%20a%20two-hour%20drive%20from%20home%20%E2%80%94%20where%20the%20diverse%20terrain%20and%20charming%20village%20are%20world-famous%20and%20Winter%20Olympics-worthy%20for%20good%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20moved%20to%20Singapore%20for%20work%20over%20two%20years%20ago.%20Living%20in%20a%20tropical%20climate%20meant%20we%20hadn't%20been%20snowboarding%20since.%20We'd%20been%20itching%20to%20get%20back%20onto%20fresh%20runs%2C%20and%20instead%20of%20booking%20an%20almost%2015-hour%20flight%20back%20home%2C%20we%20excitedly%20planned%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fski-japan-niseko-luxury-resort-billionaire-slopes-chalet-photos-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eski%20trip%20to%20Japan%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20our%20friends.%20The%20flight%20from%20Singapore%20to%20Tokyo%20takes%20half%20the%20time%20at%20less%20than%207%20hours.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20weeks%20ago%2C%20in%20January%2C%20we%20flew%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdos-and-donts-traveling-in-tokyo-japan-american-expat-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETokyo%20for%20a%20few%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20then%20took%20a%20domestic%20flight%20to%20Sapporo.%20The%20ride%20in%20a%20private%20taxi%20to%20Niseko%2C%20Hokkaido%20took%20around%20two%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20reasons%20Niseko%20offered%20a%20better%20experience%20than%20Whistler%2C%20but%20why%20I%20would%20still%20choose%20the%20North%20American%20ski%20resort%20over%20the%20Japanese%20ski%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E1.%20Consistently%20soft%20and%20powdery%20snow%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%