nkatsu%20curry%2C%20and%20a%20doughnut%20for%20lunch%20on%20the%20slope.%3Cp%3ETammy%20Kwan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Whistler%20and%20local%20mountains%20across%20British%20Columbia%2C%20my%20quick%20bites%20on%20the%20mountains%20usually%20consisted%20of%20mediocre%20burgers%2C%20poutines%2C%20and%20chili.%20In%20Niseko%2C%20the%20resort%20lunches%20aren't%20cheap%3A%20dishes%20range%20between%20%2417%20to%20%2424.%20But%20everything%20I%20tried%20was%20delicious%2C%20including%20tonkatsu%20curry%20rice%2C%20spicy%20miso%20ramen%2C%20charcoal-grilled%20chicken%20cartilage%2C%20and%20tempura%20soba.%20Meals%20usually%20ended%20with%20Hokkaido%20milk%20soft-serve%20ice%20cream.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20drinks%2C%20when%20we%20weren't%20in%20the%20mood%20for%20another%20cold%20beer%2C%20green%20tea%20or%20hot%20chocolate%20were%20good%20options%20at%20the%20dining%20hall.%20The%20Japanese%20vending%20machines%20never%20disappointed%20either%20with%20offerings%20like%20hot%20milk%20tea%20and%20Calpis%20soda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E3.%20Big%2C%20beautiful%2C%20and%20well-equipped%20chalets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20looking%20out%20the%20window%20at%20ski%20chalet%20in%20Niseko%2C%20Japan%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bb4383ac2de4f17ee67f15%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222269%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room%20view%20at%20Sanga%20House%20Chalet%3Cp%3ETammy%20Kwan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20traveled%20with%20a%20big%20group%2C%20we%20agreed%20it%20would%20be%20easier%20to%20book%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchalet-girl-day-in-life-courchevel-1850-ski-resort-france-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20private%20chalet%3C%2Fa%3E%20so%20everyone%20could%20hang%20out%20and%20relax%20in%20shared%20spaces.%20There%20are%20many%20different%20chalet%20and%20cabin%20options%20at%20varying%20prices%20listed%20on%20Niseko%20holiday%20rental%20websites.%20Many%20of%20these%20lodgings%20are%20newly%20built%20or%20renovated%20and%20provide%20a%20cozy%20escape%20from%20the%20cold%20winter%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20chalet%20came%20with%20a%20direct%20view%20of%20Mount%20Yotei%20(weather%20permitting)%2C%20an%20eight-person%20vehicle%2C%20a%20heated%20jacket%20and%20boot%20storage%20room%2C%20snowboard%20and%20ski%20racks%2C%20a%20fully%20equipped%20kitchen%20and%20utensils%2C%20and%20a%20fireplace.%20It%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20splurge%2C%20but%20nothing%20good%20comes%20cheap%20in%20Niseko%20%E2%80%94%20it%20was%20around%20%24185%20per%20night%2C%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Homecooked%20Japanese%20meals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223019%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wagyu%20beef%20and%20other%20ingredients%20for%20Japanese%20homecooking.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bb40e57a3d27148876715e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222526%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuality%20Wagyu%20beef%20from%20the%20local%20supermarket%20for%20homecooking.%3Cp%3ETammy%20Kwan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20apr%C3%A8s-ski%20food%20options%20were%20difficult%20to%20navigate%2C%20as%20many%20dining%20establishments%20required%20advance%20reservations.%20During%20our%20five%20days%20in%20Niseko%2C%20we%20only%20made%20one%20restaurant%20booking.%20Despite%20being%20one%20of%20the%20more%20highly%20rated%20izakaya%20establishments%2C%20we%20all%20agred%20that%20the%20food%20was%20the%20food%20was%20so-so%20and%20not%20worth%20the%20price.%20I%20paid%20%2433%20for%20a%20few%20small%20appetizers%2C%20and%20other%20friends%20paid%20around%20%2470%20per%20person%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-japanese-foods-2019-1%23shabu-shabu-is-fun-to-eat-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshabu%20shabu%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20sides%20of%20sashimi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20decided%20to%20venture%20to%20Lucky%20Supermarket%20in%20nearby%20Kutchan%2C%20which%20was%20an%208-minute%20drive%20away%20from%20our%20chalet.%20The%20grocer%20was%20stocked%20with%20everything%20from%20wagyu%20beef%2C%20fresh%20seafood%20and%20sushi%20to%20fresh%20fruits%20and%20veggies%20%E2%80%94%20perfect%20for%20making%20our%20own%20sukiyaki%20and%20shabu%20shabu%20dinner%20at%20home.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20tray%20of%20fatty%20wagyu%20beef%20cost%20around%207%2C200%20Yen%20or%20%2449%2C%20which%20was%20more%20than%20enough%20for%20three%20people.%20Eating%20these%20types%20of%20meals%20out%20in%20Niseko%20would%20have%20cost%20us%20at%20least%20triple%20the%20price%2C%20and%20it%20was%20more%20enjoyable%20to%20stay%20cozy%20and%20cook%20at%20the%20chalet%20with%20our%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5.%20Hot%20springs%20to%20help%20relax%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223944%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Snow%20covered%20parking%20lot%20outside%20an%20onsen%2C%20Japanese%20bath%2C%20in%20Japan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bb40e67a3d271488767160%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222969%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20Niseko%20Grand%20Hotel%20Hokkaido%20for%20the%20day-use%20onsen%3Cp%3ETammy%20Kwan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-travel-leisure-best-destination-photos-2018-12%23take-a-dip-in-this-1300-year-old-hotels-natural-hot-springs-14%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOnsens%2C%20or%20Japanese%20hot%20spring%20baths%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20are%20not%20the%20norm%20in%20Whistler.%20Around%20Niseko%2C%20a%20handful%20of%20these%20bathing%20facilities%20use%20naturally%20hot%20water%20from%20geothermally%20heated%20springs.%20Many%20people%20believe%20various%20health%20benefits%20are%20associated%20with%20soaking%20in%20these%20hot%20indoor%20and%20outdoor%20baths.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnsen%20etiquette%20is%20also%20unique%3A%20men%20and%20women%20are%20separated%20into%20different%20hot%20spring%20facilities%2C%20everyone%20must%20fully%20wash%20and%20rinse%20their%20bodies%20before%20entering%20the%20baths%2C%20and%20no%20clothing%20is%20allowed.%20It%20wasn't%20my%20first%20time%20visiting%20an%20onsen%2C%20but%20it%20still%20took%20some%20time%20to%20get%20used%20to%20%E2%80%94%20I%20don't%20often%20get%20fully%20naked%20with%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20noticed%20that%20my%20sore%20muscles%20felt%20more%20relaxed%20after%20visiting%20an%20onsen%20at%20the%20end%20of%20each%20night%20and%20it%20would%20help%20prepare%20me%20for%20another%20full%20day%20of%20snowboarding%20the%20next%20morning.%20Watching%20the%20snow%20fall%20into%20the%20misty%20outdoor%20hot%20spring%20bath%20was%20also%20something%20I%20won't%20soon%20forget.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFinal%20Verdict%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224044%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Clear%20view%20of%20Mount%20Yotei%20in%20Niseko%2C%20Japan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bb40e57a3d27148876715f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223045%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClear%20view%20of%20Mount%20Yotei%20in%20Niseko%2C%20Japan.%3Cp%3ETammy%20Kwan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20got%20to%20snowboard%20in%20Niseko%2C%20Hokkaido%20at%20least%20once%20in%20my%20life%2C%20and%20experience%20its%20renowned%20powdery%20snow.%20Although%20Niseko%20has%20many%20pros%2C%20I%20couldn't%20help%20compare%20it%20to%20Whistler%20every%20chance%20I%20got.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20snow%20in%20Whistler%20isn't%20as%20consistent%2C%20it%20surpasses%20the%20Japanese%20ski%20town%20for%20many%20reasons.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-ski-resorts-banff-ranking-price-amenities-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECanadian%20ski%20resort%3C%2Fa%3E%2