To%20provide%20maximum%20comfort%2C%20the%20best%20slippers%20for%20men%20will%20need%20to%20differ%20in%20many%20ways%20from%20whatever%20shoes%20you've%20been%20wearing%20all%20day.%20%26quot%3BThe%20body%20and%20feet%20love%20moderation%20and%20variety%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Sutera.%C2%A0%20Wearing%20the%20same%20shoes%20all%20day%20and%20everyday%20is%20not%20healthy%20in%20the%20long%20run.%20This%20can%20lead%20to%20overuse%20and%20repetitive%20stress%20injuries%20such%20as%20tendonitis%2C%20plantar%20fasciitis%2C%20just%20to%20name%20a%20few.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20dress%20shoes%20or%20work%20boots%2C%20stepping%20into%20a%20pair%20of%20slippers%20with%20a%20deep%20heel%20cup%20and%20extra%20arch%20cushion%20will%20provide%20significant%20relief%2C%20especially%20when%20worn%20routinely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20slippers%20are%20best%20for%20plantar%20fasciitis%20or%20high%20arches%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20the%20best%20slippers%20for%20men%20with%20plantar%20fasciitis%2C%20Dr.%20Sutera%20developed%20the%20%26quot%3BTabletop%20Test.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BTake%20your%20shoes%2C%20put%20them%20on%20a%20tabletop%20and%20examine%20the%20soles%20at%20eye%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20tells%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAre%20they%20even%3F%20Are%20they%20worn%3F%20Then%20flip%20them%20upside%20down%20and%20examine%20the%20tread.%20Is%20it%20smooth%3F%20Does%20it%20have%20holes%3F%20If%20so%2C%20replace%20the%20shoes.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20to%20avoid%20any%20flimsiness%20and%20instead%20wear%20slippers%20that%20provide%20ample%20shock%20absorption.%20Sore%20high%20arches%20similarly%20need%20extra%20cushioning%2C%20though%20it's%20equally%20important%20for%20the%20slippers%20to%20feel%20somewhat%20flexible%20to%20accommodate%20the%20foot's%20natural%20shape.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20the%20best%20materials%20for%20slippers%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20trying%20to%20find%20the%20right%20pair%20of%20slippers%2C%20consider%20which%20materials%20will%20accommodate%20your%20long%20term%20needs.%20In%20cooler%20climates%20and%20seasons%2C%20wool%20and%20shearling%20will%20help%20regulate%20body%20temperature%20by%20keeping%20the%20extremities%20warm.%20For%20hot%20weather%2C%20opt%20for%20a%20slipper%20with%20a%20ventilated%20material%20to%20prevent%20any%20stuffiness.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20recommend%20a%20washable%20slipper%20which%20does%20not%20absorb%20sweat.%20This%20will%20reduce%20odor%20causing%20bacteria%20that%20would%20thrive%20in%20the%20fabric%20versions%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Sutera%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20foam%20midsoles%20in%20your%20current%20pair%20have%20become%20flat%2C%20it's%20time%20to%20start%20looking%20for%20the%20best%20slippers%20for%20men%20that'll%20fit%20true-to-size%20and%20maintain%20the%20same%20form%20and%20function%20as%20they%20day%20they%20were%20purchased.%C2%A0%20%26quot%3BWearing%20shoes%20that%20fit%20too%20tight%20or%20too%20loose%20can%20cause%20injury%20and%20pain%20over%20time.%20Bunions%20and%20hammertoes%20can%20get%20worse%2C%20and%20this%20can%20cause%20blisters%2C%20ingrown%20toenails%2C%20bruising%2C%20neuromas%2C%20and%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr.%20Sutera.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-slippers-men%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706828122000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F631a481a0a329a0011e38acc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-slippers-men%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20spoke%20with%20a%20podiatrist%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20slippers%20for%20men.%20Our%20favorite%20styles%20come%20from%20brands%20like%20UGG%2C%20Allbirds%2C%20L.L.Bean%