7a1531f6e8d88ed471c04%26postID%3D619704681734c7655274bd2b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fbest-dandruff-shampoos%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fdp%252FB00AINMFAC%5C%22%3ESee%20at%20Amazon%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Neutrogena%20T%2FGel%20Therapeutic%20Shampoo%3Cp%3EThe%20active%20ingredient%20in%20this%20shampoo%20is%20coal%20tar%20%E2%80%94%20which%20medical%20professionals%20have%20used%20for%20years%20to%20help%20treat%20forms%20of%20dermatitis%2C%20as%20it%20helps%20slow%20skin%20cell%20growth%20and%20minimizes%20dryness.%20The%20formulation%20also%20comprises%20citric%20acid%2C%20which%20is%20thought%20to%20aid%20dandruff%20thanks%20to%20its%20pH-friendly%20and%20antioxidant%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20coal%20tar%20may%20not%20emanate%20the%20most%20nose-pleasing%20scents%2C%20it%20means%20business%3A%20This%20shampoo%20has%20garnered%20nearly%2012%2C000%20five-star%20ratings%20on%20Amazon.%20It's%20strong%20stuff%2C%20meaning%20it's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dandruff%20shampoos%20that%20gets%20to%20work%20quickly%20and%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20used%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20so%20a%20bottle%20lasts%20a%20good%20while.%20Note%20that%20coal%20tar%20shampoos%20should%20be%20avoided%20if%20you're%20pregnant%20or%20breastfeeding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20drugstore%3A%20Dove%20Dermacare%20Scalp%20Anti-dandruff%20Shampoo%20and%20Conditioner%3Cp%3EWe%20all%20love%20getting%20more%20bang%20for%20our%20buck%2C%20and%20this%20delivers%20a%202-in-1%20formula.%20Dandruff%20shampoos%20may%20put%20some%20off%20due%20to%20their%20medicinal-like%20scents%2C%20but%20users%20rave%20about%20how%20nice%20this%20one%20smells.%20And%2C%20even%20better%2C%20they%20love%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20leaves%20hair%20feeling%20smoother%20and%20softer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20an%20active%20ingredient%20of%20zinc%20pyrithione%2C%20the%20formulation%20also%20contains%20anti-inflammatory%20aloe%20vera%20and%20sunflower%20seed%20to%20help%20calm%20the%20skin%2C%20cucumber%20to%20aid%20scalp%20health%2C%20and%20peppermint%20to%20moisturize.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20moisturizing%3A%20Head%20%26amp%3B%20Shoulders%20Moisturizing%20Hair%20%26amp%3B%20Scalp%20Co-Wash%3Cp%3ECurly%2C%20coily%2C%20and%20kinky%20hair%20types%20are%20no%20strangers%20to%20clarifying%20shampoos%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20if%20it's%20wash%20day%20and%20your%20scalp%20has%20been%20itching%20for%20days.%20With%20all%20the%20styling%20products%20that%20these%20hair%20types%20use%20to%20keep%20curls%20moisturized%20and%20defined%2C%20a%20good%20balancing%20shampoo%20is%20a%20must.%20This%20co-wash%20from%20Head%20and%20Shoulders%20offers%20the%20power%20of%20a%20dandruff%20shampoo%20for%20curly%20hair%2C%20without%20stripping%20hair%20of%20the%20natural%20oils%20it%20needs%20to%20stay%20nourished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZinc%20pyrithione%20is%20used%20to%20combat%20dandruff%2C%20flakiness%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC3232817%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DZinc%2520pyrithione%2520(ZPT)%2520is%2520an%2520antimicrobial%2520compound%2520that%2520has%2520been%2Cstops%2520dandruff%2520flaking%2520(6).%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efungal%20activity%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20scalp%20that%20may%20be%20causing%20you%20to%20scratch%20incessantly%20at%20your%20head.%20This%20co-wash%20relieves%20scalp%20dryness%2C%20while%20coconut%20oil%20adds%20moisture%20without%20clogging%20hair%20follicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20potent%3A%20Ryo%20Scalp%20Deep%20Cleansing%20%26amp%3B%20Cooling%20Shampoo%3Cp%3EKorean%20beauty%20practices%20are%20well-observed%20in%20the%20US%2C%20specifically%20regarding%20the%20dewy%20skin%20goals%20of%20the%20K-beauty%20trends.%20However%2C%20Korean%20haircare%20isn't%20given%20the%20same%20attention%20even%20though%20it%20is%20just%20as%20effective%20and%20beneficial%20to%20overall%20beauty%20routines.%20This%20deep%20cleansing%20shampoo%20from%20the%20Korean%20brand%20Ryo%20is%20the%20perfect%20introduction%20to%20the%20category%20for%20a%20daily%20dandruff%20wash%20that%20reduces%20excessive%20sebum%20(oil)%20while%20gently%20soothing%20the%20scalp.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFermented%20mint%20keeps%20greasy%20scalps%20at%20bay%2C%20while%20the%20added%20peppermint%20and%20pine%20needle%20extract%20offer%20mattifying%20and%20cooling%20sensations.%20This%20liquid%20formula%20quickly%20lathers%20into%20a%20gentle%20foam%20that%20easily%20covers%20the%20entire%20scalp%20with%20only%20a%20quarter-sized%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20luxury%3A%20Philip%20B.%20Anti-Flake%20Relief%20Shampoo%20Extra%20Strength%3Cp%3EPhilip%20B.%20has%20been%20synonymous%20with%20scalp%20assistance%20since%20the%20brand%20launched%20its%20first%20product%20(the%20rejuvenating%20oil%20treatment)%20in%201992.%20After%2032%20years%2C%20the%20brand%20has%20extended%20to%20include%20a%20full%20line%20of%20luxury%20hair%20care%20products%20that%20still%20put%20scalp%20health%20first.%20This%20is%20proven%20by%20their%20extra-strength%20anti-flake%20relief%20shampoo%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dandruff%20shampoos%20for%20a%20reason.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20powerful%20formulation%20of%20two%20leading%20dandruff%20ingredients%20(coal%20tar%20and%20zinc%20pyrithione)%20combined%20with%20invigorating%20tea%20tree%20oil%20and%20soothing%20aloe%20vera%20makes%20for%20the%20ultimate%20dandruff%20cleansing%20experience.%20After%20your%20first%20use%2C%20you'll%20notice%20reduced%20oil%20and%20irritation%20with%20a%20lingering%20scent%20of%20sage%20and%20juniper%20berries%20that%20adds%20to%20the%20luxe%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20scalp%20treatment%3A%20Nioxin%20Scalp%20Recovery%20Cleanser%3Cp%3EThis%20brand%20is%20best%20known%20for%20its%20hair-thickening%20products%2C%20but%20if%20you%20have%20dandruff%2C%20then%20the%20Scalp%20Recovery%20range%20is%20worth%20looking%20at.%20As%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20flake-fighting%20range%20(including%20a%20conditioner%2C%20exfoliator%2C%20and%20serum)%2C%20this%20shampoo%20contains%20zinc%20pyrithione%20to%20fight%20Malassezia%20yeast%20overgrowth.%20However%2C%20green%20tea%20extract%20and%20peppermint%20oil%20also%20help%20soothe%20the%20scalp%2C%20along%20with%20nourishing%20vitamins%20such%20as%20biotin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20like%20that%20it%20lathers%20well%20and%20thoroughly%20cleanses%20the%20hair%20and%20scalp.%20Plus%2C%20many%20reviewers%20comment%20on%20how%20effective%20it%20is%20at%20preventing%20itching%20and%20the%20appearance%20of%20flakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20sulfate-free%3A%20Jupiter%20Balancing%20Shampoo%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20five-star%20reviews%20are%20anything%20to%20go%20by%2C%20this%20dandruff-buster%20really%20is%20out-of-this-world.%20Formulated%20and%20developed%20alongside%20dermatologists%2C%20it%20comprises%20an%20array%20of%20ingredients%20to%20fight%20flakes%3A%20zinc%20pyrithione%2C%20moisturizing%20squalane%2C%20antibacterial%20green%20tea%2C%20aloe%20vera%2C%20and%20antifungal%20jujube%2C%20to%20name%20a%20few.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20dandruff%20shampoos%20can%20leave%20hair%20feeling%20%E2%80%94%20and%20looking%20%E2%80%94%20a%20bit%20dry%20and%20lackluster%2C%20but%20this%20is%20designed%20to%20ensure%20locks%20keep%20their%20shine%20and%20feel%20smooth.%20Plus%2C%20it's%20vegan%20and%20okay%20for%20those%20with%20colored%20and%20chemically%20treated%20hair.%20Want%20even%20more%3F%20The%20range%20includes%20conditioner%2C%20serum%2C%20elixir%2C%20and%20a%20mask%20for%20a%20full-on%20attack%20against%20dandruff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20sensitive%20scalps%3A%20The%20Body%20Shop%20Ginger%20Scalp%20Care%20Shampoo%3Cp%3EThis%20product%20combines%20nature's%20best%20ingredients%20to%20help%20tackle%20flakes%2C%20itching%2C%20and%20dryness.%20As%20the%20name%20reveals%2C%20the%20primary%20ingredient%20is%20ginger%2C%20which%20offers%20antimicrobial%20and%20antifungal%20properties%20and%20a%20subtle%20warming%20scent%20when%20you%20lather%20up.%20It%20also%20contains%20birch%20bark%20extract%2C%20thought%20to%20have%20antimicrobial%20properties%2C%20and%20honey%20to%20moisturize%20dry%20scalps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20formulation%20is%20suitable%20for%20all%20hair%20types%20(including%20colored-treated%20hair)%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20matching%20conditioner%20available%20for%20a%20full-on%20scalp%20cleanse.%20Plus%2C%20as%20an%20extra%20feel-good%20boost%2C%20the%20bottle%20is%20made%20from%20100%25%20recycled%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20curly%20hair%3A%20TPH%20by%20Taraji%20Master%20Cleanse%20Scalp%20Wash%3Cp%3EDesigned%20for%20all%20hair%20types%2C%20this%20cleansing%20scalp%20wash%20is%20particularly%20popular%20with%20naturally%20curly%20hair%20and%20braided%20protective%20styles.%20Contributing%20writer%20Alexis%20Gaskin%20has%20been%20using%20this%20scalp%20cleanser%20for%20three%20months%20and%20is%20amazed%20at%20the%20non-lather%20formulation%20that%20eliminates%20buildup%20and%20leaves%20behind%20a%20tingly%20sensation%20that%20isn't%20irritating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20dealing%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20product%20buildup%20and%20a%20scratchy%20scalp%20that%20won't%20go%20away%2C%20consider%20using%20this%20wash%20twice%20a%20week%20to%20rebalance%20the%20scalp%20and%20keep%20irritation%20away.%20The%20formulation%20of%20tea%20tree%20oil%2C%20eucalyptus%2C%20and%20witch%20hazel%20gently%20reduces%20oil%20without%20stripping%20hair%20of%20oil%20or%20dehydrating%20the%20scalp%20and%20makes%20it%20one%20of%20the%20best%20dandruff%20shampoos%20we've%20tried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20dry%20hair%3A%20It's%20a%2010%20Scalp%20Restore%20Miracle%20Charcoal%20Shampoo%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20thing%20that%20dry%20hair%20dealing%20with%20dandruff%20needs%20is%20a%20shampoo%20that%20strips%20hair%20of%20oil%20and%20causes%20more%20dehydration%20in%20its%20wake.%20Instead%20of%20regularly%20using%20one%20of%20the%20potent%20dandruff%20shampoos%20mentioned%20here%2C%20opt%20for%20this%20hair-restoring%20shampoo%20formulated%20without%20the%20usual%20dandruff%20shampoo%20ingredients.%20Charcoal%20and%20kaolin%20clay%20are%20the%20hero%20ingredients%20of%20this%20shampoo%20for%20its%20ability%20to%20draw%20out%20excessive%20oil%20without%20leaving%20the%20scalp%20feeling%20tight%20or%20dry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vegan%2C%20color-safe%2C%20and%20leaping%20bunny-approved%20shampoo%20works%20hard%20to%20reduce%20buildup%20without%20removing%20the%20hair's%20needed%20oils.%20Start%20by%20using%20this%20shampoo%20once%20a%20week%20if%20you're%20currently%20dealing%20with%20dandruff%2C%20and%20follow%20up%20with%20the%20matching%20conditioner%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbiauto-51756-20%26h%3D5cb12ead54b57c34c605f49effc33784319bc73c2b20a60a3403e68c553aea77%26postID%3D619704681734c7655274bd2b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fbeauty%252Fbest-dandruff-shampoos%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.ulta.com%252Fp%252Fscalp-restore-miracle-tingling-conditioner-pimprod2033467%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt's%20A%2010%20Scalp%20Restore%20Miracle%20Tingling%20Conditioner%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20add%20back%20any%20moisture%20you%20may%20have%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20for%20oily%20hair%3A%20Vichy%20Dercos%20Anti-dandruff%20Shampoo%3Cp%3EThis%20shampoo%20comes%20as%20another%20recommendation%20from%20Dr.%20Therianou%2C%20this%20time%20thanks%20to%20the%20salicylic%20acid%20content%20%E2%80%94%20an%20ingredient%20she%20advises%20for%20calming%20dandruff.%20It's%20been%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8528166%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproven%20in%20studies%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20break%20d