his%20regard%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20Jaiswal%20omitted%20any%20reference%20to%20cutting%20funds%20to%20the%20UN%20agency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20met%20its%20annual%20contribution%20of%20%245%20million%20to%20UNRWA%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22about%3Ablank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehanding%20over%20%242.5%20million%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20last%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.un.org%2Fen%2F2024%2Fsc15575.doc.htm%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20UN%20Security%20Council%20meeting%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20UN%20Under-Secretary-General%20for%20Humanitarian%20Affairs%20and%20Emergency%20Relief%20Coordinator%2C%20Martin%20Griffith%20urged%20the%20countries%20to%20resume%20their%20funding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20pre-empt%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20investigation%20or%20to%20take%20measures%20that%20effectively%20amount%20to%20the%20collective%20punishment%20of%2030%2C000%C2%A0UNRWA%20staff%20and%20millions%20of%20refugees%20beneficiaries%20of%20UNRWA%20services%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGriffith%20described%20UNRWA%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbeating%20heart%E2%80%9D%20of%20all%20humanitarian%20work%20in%20Gaza.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20this%2C%20even%20as%20its%20own%20staff%20are%20being%20killed%2C%20injured%20and%20displaced.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20stated%20that%20number%20of%20people%20killed%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20military%20operation%20in%20Gaza%20has%20likely%20crossed%2026%2C000%2C%20most%20of%20them%20women%20and%20children.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706809701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06143503%2Fimage1170x530cropped-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld