80%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68171280.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-us-canada-68171280.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20'Viksit%20Bharat'%2C%20Budget%20for%20Health%20and%20Nutrition%20Declines%20in%20Real%20Terms%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01221118%2F4904202292_1f45546edc_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20interim%20budget%20presented%20for%20the%20year%202024-25%2C%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20pitched%20for%20a%20%E2%80%98Viksit%20Bharat%E2%80%99%20by%202047.%20However%2C%20in%20that%20imagination%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98developed%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20budget%20allocation%20for%20the%20department%20of%20health%20and%20family%20welfare%20and%20the%20department%20of%20health%20research%2C%20and%20key%20nutrition%20programmes%20have%20dipped%20for%20the%20FY%202024-25%20as%20compared%20to%20FY%202023-24%20budget%20estimates%2C%20when%20adjusted%20for%20inflation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20two%20departments%20related%20to%20health%20come%20under%20Ministry%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%2C%20while%20nutrition%20schemes%20are%20managed%20by%20Ministry%20of%20Woman%20and%20Child%20Development.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAgainst%20the%20allocation%20of%20Rs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E86%2C175%20crores%20(according%20to%20budget%20estimates)%20for%20the%20department%20of%20health%20and%20family%20welfare%20for%20FY%202023-24%2C%20the%20allocation%20for%202024-25%20stood%20at%20Rs%2087%2C656%20crore.%20While%20this%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20increase%20in%20absolute%20numbers%2C%20when%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%20at%20even%205%25%2C%20this%20is%20a%20decline%20of%203.17%25.%20Thus%2C%20in%20real%20terms%2C%20the%20budget%20for%20the%20health%20and%20family%20welfare%20department%20has%20gone%20down.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20National%20Health%20Policy%2C%202017%2C%20India%20needs%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eincrease%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20its%20budget%20for%20health%20every%20year%20so%20as%20to%20meet%20the%20target%20of%20spending%202.5%25%20of%20the%20GDP%20on%20health%20by%20the%20year%202025.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPMSSY%20among%20worst%20hit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20key%20programmes%20that%20was%20hit%20was%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Swasthya%20Suraksha%20Yojana%20under%20the%20department%20of%20health%20and%20family%20welfare.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Swasthya%20Suraksha%20Yojana%20(PMSSY)%20envisages%20the%20creation%20of%20tertiary%20healthcare%20capacity%20in%20medical%20education%2C%20research%20and%20clinical%20care%2C%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eunder-served%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20areas%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20official%20document.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20FY%202024-25%2C%20the%20scheme%20has%20been%20allocated%20Rs%202%2C400%20crore%20as%20against%20the%20budget%20estimate%20of%20Rs%203%2C365%20crore%20for%20the%20last%20financial%20year.%20This%20essays%20a%20decline%20of%2033%25%20even%20without%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20inflation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20aims%20to%20upgrade%20existing%20medical%20colleges%20across%20India%20and%20build%20new%20AIIMS-like%20institutions.%20Six%20of%20these%20include%20the%20ones%20which%20were%20conceptualised%20during%20the%20last%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee-led%20government.%20Another%2016%20were%20conceptualised%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20NDA%20government%20which%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20government%20constantly%20claims%20that%20establishment%20of%20new%20AIIMS-like%20institutions%20has%20been%20one%20of%20its%20biggest%20achievements%20but%20according%20to%20a%20parliamentary%20reply%20given%20last%20year%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fpm-modi-aiims-functioning%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20not%20one%20of%20the%2016%20institutes%20conceived%20from%202014%20is%20fully%20functional%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eyet.%20And%2C%20now%20even%20the%20budgetary%20allocation%20has%20been%20slashed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20a%20separate%20head%20in%20the%20budget%20document%20titled%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98Establishment%20Expenditure%20of%20New%20AIIMS%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20provides%20for%20establishment%20expenditure%20of%2022%20new%20AIIMS%20located%20at%20different%20states%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20document%20says.%20Under%20this%20head%20too%2C%20the%20budget%20estimates%20for%20FY%202024-25%20have%20declined%20to%20Rs%206%2C800%20crore%20from%20Rs%206%2C835%20crore%20(budget%20estimates)%20for%20the%20previous%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20department%20of%20health%20research%20and%20is%20the%20most%20prominent%20research%20body%20for%20health%20and%20science%2C%20has%20been%20allocated%20Rs%202%2C432%20crore%20for%20FY%202024-25%20as%20against%20Rs%202%2C360%20crore%20for%20last%20year.%20Again%2C%20while%20in%20absolute%20numbers%2C%20this%20seems%20to%20be%20an%20increase%2C%20but%20when%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%20for%20even%205%25%2C%20it%20is%20a%20decline%20of%201.87%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allocation%20for%20National%20Aids%20and%20Sexually%20Transmitted%20Diseases%20(STDs)%20control%20programme%20also%20decreased%20to%20Rs%203%2C049%20crore%20for%20FY%202024-25%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20a%20decline%20of%201%25%20as%20compared%20to%20previous%20year%E2%80%99s%20allocation%20but%20the%20shortfall%20is%20more%20than%205%25%20when%20adjusted%20with%20inflation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAyushman%20Bharat%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Health%20Infrastructure%20Mission%20(PM-ABHIM)%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fhealth%2Fcentre-s-rs-64-000-cr-plan-for-future-pandemics-what-does-it-consist-of--79889%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elaunched%20in%202021%20after%20the%20massive%20second%20wave%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20scheme%20was%20aimed%20at%20preparing%20for%20future%20pandemics.%20At%20the%20time%20of%20launch%20it%20aimed%20at%20spending%20Rs%2064%2C000%20crore%20over%20a%20span%20of%20five%20years.%20This%20also%20saw%20a%20decline%20in%20allocation%20as%20compared%20to%20budget%20estimates%20for%20last%20year.%20It%20has%20been%20allocated%20Rs%204%2C107%20crore%20for%20FY%202024-25%20as%20compared%20to%20Rs%204%2C200%20crore%20last%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20measures%20under%20the%20PM%20ABHIM%20focus%20on%20developing%20capacities%20of%20health%20systems%20and%20institutions%20across%20the%20continuum%20of%20care%20at%20all%20levels%2C%20primary%2C%20secondary%20and%20tertiary%2C%20to%20prepare%20health%20systems%20in%20responding%20effectively%20to%20the%20current%20and%20future%20pandemics%2Fdisaster%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20budget%20document.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20launched%20a%20scheme%20to%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20branches%20of%20National%20Center%20for%20Disease%20Control%20(NCDC).%20Currently%20there%20is%20only%20one%20branch%20at%20Delhi.%20The%20NCDC%20was%20supposed%20to%20play%20an%20important%20role%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20that%20head%20itself%2C%20the%20government%20had%20planned%20to%20control%20zoonotic%20diseases%20(diseases%20jumping%20from%20animals%20to%20humans)%2C%20and%20strengthen%20efforts%20to%20reign%20in%20antibiotic%20resistance%2C%20technically%20known%20as%20antimicrobial%20resistance%20(AMR).%20India%20has%20the%20highest%20burden%20of%20AMR%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20allocation%20in%20this%20head%20too%20stood%20slashed%20from%20Rs%2055.52%20crore%20to%20Rs%2052%20crore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20scheme%2C%20which%20saw%20an%20increase%20almost%20nearly%20adjusted%20with%20inflation%20was%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(PMJAY)%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20is%20a%20part.%20The%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme%20provides%20an%20insurance%20cover%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20family%20per%20year%20for%20the%20hospitalisation%20expenses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20PMJAY%20scheme%20has%20covered%2040%25%20families%20of%20India.%20The%20insurance%20premium%20is%20paid%20by%20the%20Central%20and%20the%20state%20governments%20as%20it%20is%20a%20centrally%20sponsored%20scheme.%20The%20scheme%20has%20been%20allocated%20Rs%207%2C500%20crore%20for%20FY%202024-25%20as%20against%20allocation%20of%20Rs%207%2C200%20crore%20for%20FY%202023-24%20(BE).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20government%20touts%20the%20PMJAY%20as%20a%20landmark%20scheme%2C%20it%20receives%20criticism%20for%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20create%20infrastructure%20and%20put%20money%20in%20hands%20of%20private%20healthcare%20providers.%20However%2C%20the%20government%20counters%20this%20by%20saying%20it%20has%20also%20built%20more%20than%201.5%20lakh%20health%20and%20wellness%20centres.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20had%20found%20the%20scheme%20riddled%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fayushman-bharat-cag-report-pmjay-corruption%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evarious%20forms%20of%20corruption%20at%20multiple%20levels%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20causing%20not%20just%20loss%20to%20the%20exchequer%20but%20defeating%20the%20purpose%20of%20the%20scheme.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENutrition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20finance%20minister%20stressed%20in%20her%20speech%20that%20Poshan%202.0%20will%20be%20expedited%20for%20improved%20nutrition%20delivery%2C%20early%20childhood%20care%20and%20development.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPoshan%202.0%20and%20Saksham%20Anganwadi%20scheme%20aims%20at%20%E2%80%9Cto%20develop%20practices%20that%20nurture%20health%2C%20wellness%20and%20immunity%20among%20malnutrition.%E2%80%9D%20India%20is%20home%20to%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20malnourished%20children%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20scheme%20has%20been%20allocated%20Rs%2021%2C200%20crore%20for%20FY%202024-25%2C%20an%20increase%20from%20Rs%2020%2C554.31%20crore%20(budget%20estimates)%20from%20previous%20financial%20year.%20However%2C%20when%20adjusted%20with%20inflation%20of%205%25%2C%20this%20allocation%20is%20actually%20a%20decline%20of%201.77%25.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERecently%2C%20India%20was%20ranked%20111%20out%20of%20125%20countries%20in%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Findia-ranks-111th-among-125-countries-in-global-hunger-index-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGlobal%20Hunger%20Index%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20The%20government%20rubbished%20the%20report%20though%20the%20report%20makers%20stood%20by%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20budget%20speech%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20said%20that%20the%20government%20would%20%E2%80%98encourage%E2%80%99%20girls%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%209-14%20years%20to%20take%20the%20HPV%20vaccine%20for%20the%20prevention%20of%20cervical%20cancer.%20However%2C%20she%20did%20not%20spell%20out%20whether%20the%20HPV%20vaccine%20%E2%80%93%20the%20jab%20against%20the%20cancer%20%E2%80%93%20would%20become%20a%20part%20of%20routine%20immunisation%20programme%20of%20the%20government%20given%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20government%20itself%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleaseIframePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1995855%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20few%20days%20ago%20that%20there%20were%20no%20immediate%20plans%20to%20introduce%20it%20in%20such%20a%20way%20in%20the%20later%20part%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnganwadi%20and%20ASHA%20workers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20also%20said%20a%20committee%20would%20be%20set%20up%20to%20open%20more%20medical%20colleges.%20However%2C%20no%20more%20details%20were%20given.%20It%20may%20be%20mentioned%20here%20that%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Swasthya%20Suraksha%20Yojana%2C%20the%20government%20is%20already%20aiming%20at%20developing%20more%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20announced%20that%20the%20ASHA%20and%20Anganwadi%20workers%20would%20be%20extended%20the%20cover%20of%20Ayushman%20Bharat.%20The%20ASHAs%2C%20who%20are%20designated%20as%20activists%2C%20have%20been%20constantly%20demanding%20that%20they%20be%20given%20the%20status%20of%20workers%20so%20that%20they%20can%20get%20the%20cover%20of%20social%20security%20schemes%20which%20government%20workers%20get.%20Though%20that%20demand%20remains%20unmet%2C%20this%20may%20be%20the%20first%20instance%20of%20people%20employed%20by%20the%20government%20being%20extended%20the%20insurance%20cover%20of%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20scheme.%20Union%20government%20employees%20are%20covered%20under%20the%20central%20government%20health%20scheme%20or%20CGHS%2C%20which%20unlike%20a%20health%20insurance%20scheme%2C%20gives%20upfront%20subsidised%20healthcare%20%E2%80%94%20both%20OPD%20and%20hospitalisation%20%E2%80%94%20to%20all%20its%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706805863000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F01221118%2F4904202292_1f45546edc_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbudget-interim-health-nutrition-declines%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20the%20allocation%20for%20departments%20of%20health%20and%20family%20welfare%2C%20and%20health%20research%2C%20along%20with%20nutrition%20schemes%2C%20seem%20to%20have%20increased%20in%20absolute%20numbers%2C%20but%20when%20adjusted%20for%20inflation%2C%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20decline.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fbudget-interim-health-nutrition-declines%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IHCL%20Q3%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20rises%2018%25%20to%20Rs%20452%20crore%2C%20revenue%20up%2014.1%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706805836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2016-12%2F20%2Ffull%2F1482236916-5678.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fihcl-q3-results-net-profit-rises-18-to-rs-452-crore-revenue-up-14-1-124020101924_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20hospitality%20giant%20reported%20a%2014.1%20per%20cent%20uptick%20in%20revenue%20to%20Rs%201%2C963.24%20crore%20from%20Rs%201%2C685.80%20crore%20in%20the%20year-ago%20period%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fihcl-q3-results-net-profit-rises-18-to-rs-452-crore-revenue-up-14-1-124020101924_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fihcl-q3-results-net-profit-rises-18-to-rs-452-crore-revenue-up-14-1-124020101924_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanie