%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vibrations%20of%20the%20spectacle%20of%20inauguration%20of%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20temple%20are%20still%20in%20the%20air.%20This%20inauguration%20was%20done%20by%20Prime%20Minster%20Narendra%20Modi%20who%20was%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20whole%20ceremony.%20In%20this%20instance%20he%20represented%20both%20%E2%80%98state%20power%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98religious%20power%E2%80%99.%20In%20feudal%20times%20these%20two%20were%20working%20in%20close%20collaboration%2C%20boosting%20each%20other.%20There%20was%20King-Pope%2C%20%3Cem%3ENawab-%20Shahi%20Imam%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%3Cem%3E%20Raja-Rajguru%3C%2Fem%3E.%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20there%20is%20a%20very%20apt%20rhyming%20of%20this%20collaboration%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3EShetji-Bhatji%3C%2Fem%3E%20(landlord%20and%20priest).%20That%20the%20country%2C%20ruled%20by%20politics%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%20is%20seeing%20this%20trajectory%20fructifying%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20deep%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20India%20became%20independent%20and%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20came%20into%20being%2C%20the%20presence%20of%20religion%20in%20social%20spaces%20was%20very%20much%20there.%20So%20when%20Dr%20Rajendra%20Prasad%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20president%2C%20was%20planning%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20Somnath%20temple%20as%20the%20official%20head%20of%20the%20state%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20wrote%20to%20him%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20confess%20that%20I%20do%20not%20like%20the%20idea%20of%20you%20associating%20yourself%20with%20a%20spectacular%20opening%20of%20the%20Somnath%20Temple.%20This%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fassembly-elections-2017%2Fstory%2Fpm-narendra-modi-vs-rahul-gandhi-over-somnath-why-nehru-opposed-rajendra-prasads-temple-visit-1097262-2017-11-30%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1707113293000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw04u8lVBjNhBeL37MGGvMbE%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%253Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fassembly-elections-2017%2Fstory%2Fpm-narendra-modi-vs-rahul-gandhi-over-somnath-why-nehru-opposed-rajendra-prasads-temple-visit-1097262-2017-11-30%2526source%253Dgmail-imap%2526ust%253D1707113293000000%2526usg%253DAOvVaw04u8lVBjNhBeL37MGGvMbE%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706862288833000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2XT1uQEf5sfkTGDN6e0lmh%5C%22%3Enot%20merely%3C%2Fa%3E%20visiting%20a%20temple%2C%20which%20can%20certainly%20be%20done%20by%20you%20or%20anyone%20else%20but%20rather%20participating%20in%20a%20significant%20function%20which%20unfortunately%20has%20a%20number%20of%20implications.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20seven%20decades%20down%20the%20line%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20inaugurated%20the%20temple%20with%20pomp%20and%20show%20and%20the%20president%2C%20Draupadi%20Murmu%2C%20was%20an%20appreciative%20onlooker%20from%20her%20vast%20Rashtrapati%20Niwas.%20The%20Union%20Cabinet%20not%20only%20hailed%20this%20act%20but%20went%20a%20step%20further%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fcabinet-hails-modi-countrys-body-got-freedom-in-1947-soul-on-jan-22-2024-9126442%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCongratulating%2520Prime%2520Minister%2520Narendra%2520Modi%2C%252C%25202024%25E2%2580%259D%252C%2520and%2520%25E2%2580%259Ceveryone%5C%22%3Epass%20a%20resolution%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6the%20body%20of%20the%20country%20attained%20Independence%20in%201947%E2%80%A6the%20Pran%20Pratishtha%20(consecration%20of%20the%20temple)%20was%20done%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024%E2%80%A6%20The%20Ram%20temple%20movement%20has%20united%20the%20country%20as%20never%20before%20and%20it%20is%20the%20day%20when%20India%E2%80%99s%20soul%20got%20freedom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fto-combat-hysteria-around-ram-mandir-an-inclusive-idea-of-india-must-be-reinforced%5C%22%3ETo%20Combat%20Communal%20Hysteria%2C%20the%20Idea%20of%20Inclusive%20India%20Must%20Be%20Reinforced%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shows%20the%20erosion%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20secular%20values%20which%2C%20so%20far%2C%20were%20held%20up%20by%20the%20state%2C%20though%20in%20a%20compromised%20way.%20However%2C%20now%20the%20word%20secular%20itself%20has%20become%20taboo.%20Even%20Nehru%20at%20that%20time%20had%20realised%20that%20while%20the%20Constitution%20is%20based%20on%20secular%20values%2C%20the%20society%20is%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20religiosity.%20So%20he%20advised%20the%20president%20not%20to%20inaugurate%20the%20Somnath%20Temple%20in%20his%20official%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20period%20of%20%E2%80%98slavery%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20ideological%20cohorts%20have%20been%20saying%20that%20India%20was%20a%20slave%20for%20over%20a%201%2C000%20years.%20This%20implies%20that%20the%20period%20when%20the%20Muslim%20kings%20ruled%20was%20a%20period%20of%20slavery.%20How%20do%20we%20define%20slavery%20in%20a%20country%20or%20a%20region%3F%20Broadly%2C%20two%20major%20criterions%20can%20be%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20when%20the%20region%20is%20being%20controlled%20from%20outside.%20But%20the%20Muslim%20kings%20who%20ruled%20India%20settle%20here%20and%20ruled%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20local%20landlords%20and%20kings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20major%20criterion%20is%20if%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20wealth%20was%20drained%20out.%20The%20period%20of%20Muslim%20rule%20did%20not%20see%20any%20such%20phenomenon.%20It%20was%20observed%20during%20the%20British%20period.%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20in%20his%20book%2C%20%3Cem%3EAn%20Era%20of%20Darkness%3A%20The%20British%20Empire%20in%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Etells%20us%20the%20drain%20of%20wealth%20from%20India%20to%20England%20during%20this%20period.%20British%20rule%20was%20the%20period%20of%20slavery%20on%20both%20these%20counts.%20Some%20Muslim%20plunderers%20did%20come%20but%20never%20stayed%20back%20to%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20question%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20soul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20soul%20of%20India%20lies%20in%20the%20values%20which%20were%20the%20base%20of%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20The%20soul%20of%20India%20also%20lies%20in%20the%20movements%20which%20accompanied%20and%20ran%20parallel%20to%20the%20freedom%20movement.%20These%20were%20the%20movements%20of%20workers%20and%20farmers%3B%20these%20were%20the%20movements%20for%20social%20equality.%20India%E2%80%99s%20soul%20was%20built%20on%20the%20foundation%20of%20the%20Indian%20civilisation%20which%20is%20well%20described%20by%20Nehru%20as%20%E2%80%9Csome%20ancient%20palimpsest%20on%20which%20layer%20upon%20layer%20of%20thought%20and%20reverie%20had%20been%20inscribed%2C%20and%20yet%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1055510%2Fnehru-and-the-spirit-of-india-a-timely-study-of-a-vision-for-a-secular-and-tolerant-india%2523%3A~%3Atext%253DNehru%252520sought%252520to%252520convey%252520this%2Cwhat%252520had%252520been%252520written%252520previously.%2525E2%252580%25259D%26source%3Dgmail-imap%26ust%3D1707113293000000%26usg%3DAOvVaw1oPVvSz5WnA6inTHBtqEah%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%253Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1055510%2Fnehru-and-the-spirit-of-india-a-timely-study-of-a-vision-for-a-secular-and-tolerant-india%252523%3A~%3Atext%25253DNehru%25252520sought%25252520to%25252520convey%25252520this%2Cwhat%25252520had%25252520been%25252520written%25252520previously.%252525E2%25252580%2525259D%2526source%253Dgmail-imap%2526ust%253D1707113293000000%2526usg%253DAOvVaw1oPVvSz5WnA6inTHBtqEah%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1706862288833000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2j0s5UZTyWVLRkDK5Fa8k6%5C%22%3Eno%20succeeding%3C%2Fa%3E%20layer%20had%20completely%20hidden%20or%20erased%20what%20had%20been%20written%20previously%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20freedom%20movement%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20farmers%E2%80%99%20movements%20(Bardoli%20and%20Champaran%20among%20others)%2C%20labour%20movements%20led%20by%20Narayan%20Meghaji%20Lokhande%20and%20Com.%20Singarvelu%2C%20and%20struggles%20for%20social%20equality%20in%20terms%20of%20caste%20and%20gender.%20Visionaries%20like%20Jyotirao%20Phule%2C%20Savitribai%20Phule%2C%20Bhimrao%20Ambedkar%2C%20and%20Ramasami%20Periyar%20Naicker%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20transforming%20Indian%20society%20from%20a%20%E2%80%98feudal-like%E2%80%99%20structure%20to%20one%20aspiring%20for%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fthe-making-of-a-temple-state-and-what-we-have-done-to-deserve-it%5C%22%3EThe%20Making%20of%20a%20Temple%20State%20and%20What%20We%20have%20Done%20to%20Deserve%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Constitution%20is%20the%20embodiment%20of%20%E2%80%98soul%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20people.%20Those%20who%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20freedom%20movement%20were%20the%20ones%20who%20upheld%20the%20caste%20and%20gender%20hierarchy%20of%20the%20past.%20These%20were%20the%20social%20classes%20that%20were%20against%20caste%20and%20gender%20equality%20as%20well%20as%20the%20rights%20of%20farmers%20and%20workers.%20These%20were%20precisely%20the%20forces%20which%20asserted%20the%20politics%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Muslim%20League%2C%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Muslim%20League%20contended%20that%20Muslims%20were%20the%20rulers%2C%20whereas%20the%20Hindu%20Mahasabha-RSS%20asserted%20India%20as%20a%20Hindu%20Nation%2C%20denouncing%20Islam%20and%20Christianity%20as%20foreign%20religions.%20Surendra%20Nath%20Bannerjee%2C%20in%20his%20book%20%3Cem%3EIndia%3A%20Nation%20in%20the%20Making%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20articulated%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20sentiments%20as%20it%20shaped%20itself%20around%20the%20values%20of%20Liberty%2C%20Equality%20and%20Fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20however%2C%20claims%20of%20Ram%20being%20the%20uniting%20figure%20are%20being%20made.%20Ram%20has%20many%20interpretations.%20A%20mythological%20figure%20presented%20by%20Valmiki%20and%20later%20popularised%20by%20Goswami%20Tulisdas%20is%20one%20interpretation.%20Kabir%20saw%20Ram%20as%20the%20embodiment%20of%20universal%20humanism%20while%20Gandhi%20saw%20him%20as%20a%20uniting%20figure.%20The%20RSS%20and%20BJP%20have%20interpreted%20him%20as%20an%20exclusionary%20figure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20campaign%20for%20this%20temple%20has%20exacted%20a%20toll%2C%20evident%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20numerous%20lives%2C%20societal%20polarisation%2C%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20minorities%2C%20and%20the%20exacerbated%20plight%20of%20Dalits%2C%20Adivasis%2C%20women%2C%20and%20workers%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades.%20It%20is%20also%20reflects%20in%20the%20social%20indices%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20Muslim%20ghettos%20all%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20an%20attack%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20soul%20which%20emerged%20during%20the%20freedom%20movement%20while%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20presents%20a%20distorted%20version%20that%20revolves%20around%20a%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERam%20Puniyani%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706794247000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-indian-constitution-is-the-soul-of-india-not-ram%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Today%2C%20we%20are%20witnessing%20an%20attack%20on%20India's%20soul%20which%20emerged%20during%20the%20freedom%20movement%20while%20the%20ruling%20dispensation%20presents%20a%20distorted%20version%20that%20revolves%20around%20a%20temple.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fthe-indian-constitution-is-the-soul-of-india-not-ram%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistan%20elections%20will%20take%20place%20on%20February%208%20despite%20security%20challenges%3A%20Election%20Commission%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706794027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107331553%2Cimgsize-1786856.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fgeneral-elections-in-pakistan-confirmed-for-february-8-interior-minister%2Farticleshow%2F107331240.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107331240.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fgeneral-elections-in-pakistan-confirmed-for-february-8-interior-minister%2Farticleshow%2F107331240.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fgeneral-elections-in-pakistan-confirmed-for-february-8-interior-minister%2Famp_articleshow%2F107331240.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fgeneral-elections-in-pakistan-confirmed-for-february-8-interior-minister%2Famp_articleshow%2F107331240.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Ram%20Rajya%20Was%20No%20Hindu%20Raj%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F30082243%2FIMG_1748.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmahatma-gandhi-angel-of-history-ram-rajya-ayodhya%5C%22%3Elot%20of%20talk%20about%20Ram%20Rajya%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20even%20as%20the%20slogan%20%E2%80%98Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%99%20is%20being%20chanted%20by%20thugs%20unleashing%20violence%20against%20mosques%2C%20churches%20and%20Indians%20following%20Islam%20and%20Christianity.%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20last%20words%20when%20shot%20at%20by%20a%20Hindu%20fanatic%20on%20this%20day%20in%201948%20were%20%E2%80%98Hey%20Ram%E2%80%99%20and%20he%20would%20have%20reacted%20the%20same%20way%20at%20what%20is%20happening%20today%20in%20the%20name%20of%20Ram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20context%20of%20the%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogan%20so%20aggressively%20and%20menacingly%20recited%20on%20several%20occasions%2C%20it%20is%20instructive%20to%20recall%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20advice%20about%20such%20slogans.%20In%20an%20article%20written%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3EHarijan%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20August%209%2C%201942%2C%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20letter%20he%20received%20from%20someone%20who%20informed%20him%20that%20members%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayam%20Sevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20in%20their%20morning%20rallies%20were%20reciting%20slogans%20against%20Muslims.%20Gandhi%20wrote%20about%203%2C000%20members%20of%20RSS%20organising%20a%20daily%20lathi%20drill%20followed%20by%20reciting%20the%20slogan%2C%20%E2%80%9CHindustan%20belongs%20to%20Hindus%20and%20to%20nobody%20else.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20referred%20to%20the%C2%A0%20brief%20discourse%20accompanying%20those%20menacing%20utterances.%20During%20the%20discourse%20the%20speakers%20used%20to%20say%3A%20%E2%80%9CDrive%20out%20the%20English%20first%20and%20then%20we%20shall%20subjugate%20the%20Muslims.%20If%20they%20do%20not%20listen%2C%20we%20shall%20kill%20them.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CTaking%20the%20evidence%20at%20its%20face%20value%E2%80%9D%2C%20Gandhi%20sharply%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20slogan%20is%20wrong%20and%20the%20central%20theme%20of%20the%20discourse%20is%20worse%E2%80%9D.%20Stating%20that%20%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6.belongs%20to%20Parsis%2C%20Beni%20Israels%2C%20to%20Indian%20Christians%2C%20Muslims%20and%20other%20non-Hindus%20as%20much%20as%20to%20Hindus%E2%80%9D%2C%20Gandhi%20firmly%20rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20an%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0anchored%20in%20any%20one%20faith%20and%20categorically%20affirmed%2C%20%E2%80%9CFree%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0will%20be%20no%20Hindu%20raj%2C%20it%20will%20be%20Indian%20raj%20based%20not%20on%20the%20majority%20of%20any%20religious%20sect%20or%20community%20but%20on%20the%20representatives%20of%20the%20whole%20people%20without%20distinction%20of%20religion%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20appealed%20to%20the%20lathi%20wielding%20RSS%20activists%20to%20avoid%20reciting%20such%20violent%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20observing%20the%20solemn%C2%A0%20occasion%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20martyrdom%20day%20on%2030%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%C2%A0January%202024%20we%20need%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20those%20words%20which%20are%20more%20relevant%20in%20the%20present%20day%20when%20the%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%20slogan%20is%20being%20used%20against%20others%20pursuing%20faiths%20different%20from%20those%20of%20the%20majority%20community%20in%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Bhopal%20on%2010%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%C2%A0September%201929%2C%20Gandhi%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20his%20idea%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20was%20not%20theocratic%20in%20nature%20and%20scope%C2%A0%20and%20remarked%2C%20%E2%80%98By%20Ramarajya%E2%80%99%20I%20do%20not%20mean%20Hindu%20Raj%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CI%20mean%20by%20%E2%80%98Ramarajya%E2%80%99%20the%20Divine%20Raj%2C%20the%20Kingdom%20of%20God%E2%80%A6%20For%20me%20Rama%20and%20Rahim%20are%20one%20and%20the%20same%20deity%E2%80%9D.%20Rahim%2C%20or%20the%20merciful%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20synonyms%20of%20Allah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20acknowledge%20no%20other%20god%20but%20the%20one%20god%20of%20Truth%20and%20righteousness%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CWhether%20the%20Rama%20of%20my%20imagination%20ever%20lived%20or%20not%20on%20this%20earth%2C%20the%20ancient%20ideal%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20is%20undoubtedly%20one%20of%20true%20democracy%20in%20which%20the%20meanest%20citizen%20could%20be%20sure%20of%20swift%20justice%20without%20an%20elaborate%20and%20costly%20procedure%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20pluralistic%20nature%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20stands%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20the%20shouting%20for%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20by%20several%20of%20those%20who%20attended%20the%20consecration%20ceremony%20organised%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Ftheologically-determined-politics-weakens-representative-government%5C%22%3ETheologically%20Determined%20Politics%20Weakens%20Representative%20Government%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20idea%20of%20Hindu%20Rashtra%20was%20rejected%20by%20Gandhi%20as%20early%20as%201929%20and%20it%20is%20tragic%20that%20in%20a%20meeting%20attended%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20this%20divisive%20slogan%20was%20raised%20and%20none%20of%20the%20leaders%20attending%20that%20event%20even%20raised%20any%20objections%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERam%20Rajya%20and%20Freedom%20of%20Press%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%20defined%20Ram%20Rajya%20from%20multiple%20perspectives%2C%20one%20of%20which%20was%20the%20exercise%20of%20power%20in%20a%20regulated%20manner.%20Writing%20in%C2%A0%3Cem%3ENavajivan%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20October%2020%2C%201929%20he%20referred%20to%20the%20statement%20of%20a%20young%20man%20that%20%3Cem%3Eswaraj%3C%2Fem%3E%20meant%20the%20transfer%20of%20power%20from%20British%20hands%20to%20Indian%20hands%C2%A0%20and%20that%20it%C2%A0%20meant%20regulated%20power%20in%20the%20hands%20of%2030%20crore%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhere%20there%20is%20such%20rule%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claimed%2C%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20a%20young%20girl%20will%20feel%20herself%20safe%20and%2C%20if%20the%20imagination%20of%20a%20poet%20is%20correct%2C%20animals%20like%20dogs%2C%20etc.%2C%20who%20live%20among%20human%20beings%20will%20have%20a%20similar%20feeling%20of%20safety%E2%80%9D.%20He%20then%20explained%20that%20several%20basic%20decisions%20in%20regard%20to%20swaraj%20would%20not%20be%C2%A0%20subject%20to%20officials%20in%20power%20but%20would%20be%C2%A0%20based%20on%20truth%20and%20justice.%20Gandhi%20remarked%20that%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20succinctly%20called%20this%20kind%20of%20swaraj%20%E2%80%98Ramarajya%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20and%20added%20that%20in%20case%C2%A0%20the%20Muslims%20and%20others%20misinterpret%20it%2C%20such%20a%20Raj%20could%20be%20called%20the%20rule%20of%20dharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20talk%20of%20ushering%20in%20Ram%20Rajya%20following%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20should%20note%20that%20the%20institutions%20which%20regulate%20the%20power%20of%20the%20executive%20under%20their%20control%20have%20been%20considerably%20weakened%20to%20create%20conditions%20for%20the%20exercise%20of%20unregulated%20power%20%E2%80%93%20which%20negates%20the%20idea%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20contemplated%20by%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20two%20years%20before%20the%20attainment%20of%20independence%2C%20Gandhi%20outlined%20the%20religious%20and%20political%20dimensions%20of%20Ram%20Rajya.%20When%20one%20Sailendra%20Nath%20Chattopadhyaya%20asked%20him%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhy%20do%20you%20wish%20to%20live%20for%20125%20years%2C%20and%20what%20is%20Ram%20Rajya%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20explained%20that%20his%C2%A0wish%20to%20live%20for%20125%20years%20depended%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20selfless%20service%20he%20would%20render.%20On%20the%20issue%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20he%20explained%20that%20when%C2%A0%20religiously%20translated%20this%20meant%C2%A0%20Kingdom%20of%20God%20on%20Earth%20but%20its%20political%20components%20were%20%E2%80%9Cperfect%20democracy%20in%20which%20inequalities%20based%20on%20possession%20and%20non-possession%2C%20colour%2C%20race%20or%20creed%20or%20sex%20vanish.%E2%80%9D%20He%20went%20on%20to%20add%20that%20in%20such%20a%20Ram%20Rajya%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6land%20and%20State%20belong%20to%20the%20people%2C%20justice%20is%20prompt%2C%20perfect%20and%20cheap%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20there%20is%20freedom%20of%20worship%2C%20speech%20and%20the%20Press.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGandhi%E2%80%99s%20conception%20of%20Ram%20Rajya%20in%20terms%20of%20political%20attributes%20such%20as%20freedom%20of%20press%20should%20prompt%C2%A0our%20rulers%20to%20re-evaluate%20their%20actions%20because%20of%20which%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0ranks%20161%3Csup%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fsup%3Ein%20the%20World%20Press%20Freedom%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20Ram%20Rajya%20was%20conceived%20as%20reign%20of%20the%20self-imposed%20law%20of%20moral%20restraint.%20A%20far%20cry%20from%20the%20impunity%20and%20majoritarianism%20of%20today%E2%80%99s%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ES.N.%20%3Cspan%3ESahu%3C%2Fspan%3E%C2%A0Served%20as%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20to%20President%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%20K.R.%20Narayanan.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2