20already%20bound%20to%20do%20so%20because%20it%20is%20a%20party%20to%20the%20Genocide%20Convention.%20Therefore%2C%20Israel%20will%20likely%20continue%20its%20military%20campaign%20while%20claiming%20that%20it%20is%20compliant%20with%20applicable%20international%20law%2C%20including%20the%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20as%20it%20has%20done%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ficj-says-israel-must-comply-with-genocide-convention-but-stops-short-of-halting-military-operation%5C%22%3EICJ%20Says%20Israel%20Must%20Comply%20with%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20but%20Stops%20Short%20of%20Halting%20Military%20Op%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20also%20includes%20a%20reference%20to%20the%20events%20of%20October%207%20and%20a%20surprising%20and%20unprecedented%20call%20for%20the%20release%20of%20all%20hostages%20by%20Hamas.%20Since%20the%20ICJ%20only%20has%20jurisdiction%20over%20nation-states%2C%20it%20cannot%20legally%20bind%20the%20actions%20of%20armed%20groups%20such%20as%20Hamas.%20Further%2C%20this%20part%20of%20the%20order%20diverges%20from%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20otherwise%20clear%20and%20deliberate%20focus%20on%20matters%20within%20its%20jurisdiction%2C%20suggesting%20that%20the%20judges%20have%20been%20affected%20by%20the%20immense%20political%20pressure%20and%20propaganda%20of%20Israel%20and%20its%20allies.%20Finally%2C%20an%20overlooked%20part%20of%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20decision%20is%20its%20refusal%20to%20direct%20Israel%20to%20provide%20full%20access%20to%20fact-finding%20bodies%20such%20as%20the%20UN%20special%20procedures.%20Since%20it%20began%20its%20military%20operations%2C%20Israel%20has%20severely%20restricted%20access%20to%20the%20press%20and%20the%20UN.%20Such%20a%20measure%20may%20have%20forced%20the%20Israel%20to%20allow%20greater%20access%20to%20independent%20investigators%2C%20led%20to%20greater%20accountability%2C%20and%20possibly%20the%20discovery%20of%20more%20evidence%20against%20Israel.%20These%20are%20strong%20positives%20for%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01125649%2FUNI448902.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22770%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01125649%2FUNI448902.jpeg%20770w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F01125649%2FUNI448902-300x200.jpeg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682898%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22513%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAmal%2C%207%20years%20old%2C%20contemplates%20her%20neighbourhood%20in%20Gaza%20after%20neighbouring%20homes%20were%20levelled%20to%20the%20ground.%20Photo%3A%20UNICEF%2FMohammad%20Ajjour%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20though%20South%20Africa%20was%20not%20able%20to%20secure%20their%20main%20request%2C%20the%20order%20provides%20some%20encouragement%20for%20its%20claim.%20It%20identifies%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20as%20a%20distinct%20national%20group%2C%20an%20essential%20element%20in%20proving%20the%20crime%20of%20genocide.%20It%20also%20suggests%20that%20it%20is%20plausible%20that%20a%20real%20and%20imminent%20risk%20of%20genocide%20exists%20due%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actions%20since%207%3Csup%3Eth%3C%2Fsup%3E%20October.%20Though%20it%20is%20not%20a%20determination%20of%20liability%2C%20it%20puts%20Israel%20on%20notice.%20Crucially%2C%20the%20court%20has%20quoted%20reckless%20statements%20made%20by%20Israeli%20officials%2C%20including%20the%20President%20and%20Defence%20Minister%20holding%20all%20Palestinians%20responsible%20for%20the%20attacks%20and%20denying%20them%20the%20basic%20necessities%20of%20life.%20Since%20proving%20specific%20genocidal%20intent%20is%20the%20most%20difficult%20aspect%20of%20proving%20the%20crime%20of%20genocide%2C%20it%20is%20significant%20that%20the%20court%20recognised%20the%20plausibility%20of%20its%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20positive%20for%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20court%20made%20strong%20reference%20to%20the%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20Gaza%20and%20ordered%20that%20Israel%20must%20take%20%E2%80%9Cimmediate%20and%20effective%20measures%E2%80%9D%20to%20ensure%20humanitarian%20assistance%20is%20provided.%20Considering%20news%20of%20Israel%20blocking%20humanitarian%20aid%20from%20entering%20Gaza%2C%20this%20will%20add%20to%20the%20political%20pressure%20on%20it%20to%20allow%20all%20aid.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20President%20of%20the%20ICJ%20read%20out%20the%20statements%20of%20senior%20Israeli%20officials%20and%20concluded%20that%20it%20is%20plausible%20for%20genocide%20to%20be%20taking%20place%20is%20also%20a%20major%20victory%2C%20as%20is%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20reading%20of%20testimony%20relating%20to%20the%20dire%20situation%20in%20Gaza.%20The%20powerful%20language%20used%20by%20the%20court%20will%20help%20shape%20public%20opinion%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Palestinians%20and%20will%20increase%20pressure%20on%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20allies%20to%20reconsider%20their%20unconditional%20support%20to%20its%20military%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fby-invoking-genocide-convention-icj-makes-it-clear-israels-killing-of-palestinians-is-not-war-but-crime%5C%22%3EBy%20Invoking%20Genocide%20Convention%2C%20ICJ%20Makes%20It%20Clear%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Killing%20of%20Palestinians%20is%20Not%20%E2%80%98War%E2%80%99%20But%20Crime%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJudges%20assert%20their%20independence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20is%20a%20good%20example%20that%20the%20judges%20of%20the%20ICJ%20are%20not%20political%20representatives%20of%20their%20nominating%20States.%20This%20judicial%20independence%20is%20apparent%20in%20that%20the%20American%20President%20of%20the%20court%20voted%20in%20favour%20of%20South%20Africa%20despite%20the%20US%20being%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20closest%20ally.%20Even%20Aharon%20Barak%2C%20the%20ad-hoc%20judge%20appointed%20by%20Israel%20for%20this%20case%2C%20voted%20with%20the%20majority%20on%20the%20measures%20requiring%20Israel%20to%20prevent%20and%20punish%20any%20incitement%20of%20genocide%20against%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20and%20allow%20humanitarian%20aid.%20Closer%20to%20home%2C%20Justice%20Dalveer%20Bhandari%20of%20India%2C%20in%20a%20separate%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.icj-cij.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fcase-related%2F192%2F192-20240126-ord-01-03-en.pdf%5C%22%3Edeclaration%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stated%20that%20all%20hostages%20should%20be%20returned%20but%20also%20that%20all%20participants%20must%20ensure%20that%20hostilities%20come%20to%20an%20immediate%20halt%2C%20which%20is%20more%20supportive%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20side%20than%20the%20official%20position%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20expect%20next%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20has%20required%20that%20Israel%20must%20report%20on%20its%20compliance%20with%20provisional%20measures%20in%20one%20month%E2%80%99s%20time%2C%20and%20there%20is%20added%20pressure%20on%20Israel%20to%20allow%20humanitarian%20aid.%20Further%2C%20though%20the%20court%20has%20not%20called%20for%20halting%20hostilities%2C%20it%20may%20determine%20in%20one%20month%E2%80%99s%20time%20that%20Israel%20has%20failed%20to%20follow%20the%20provisional%20measures%20requiring%20it%20to%20prevent%20and%20punish%20incitement%20or%20commission%20of%20genocide.%20However%2C%20this%20seems%20unlikely%20considering%20that%20the%20court%20did%20not%20reach%20that%20conclusion%20at%20present%2C%20and%20the%20facts%20are%20unlikely%20to%20change%20significantly%20due%20to%20the%20massive%20scale%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20concluded%20military%20actions%2C%20which%20the%20court%20did%20not%20find%20were%20of%20sufficient%20gravity%20to%20order%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20ICJ%20cannot%20enforce%20its%20orders%2C%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20has%20the%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20compliance.%20As%20the%20US%20holds%20a%20veto%20on%20the%20Council%2C%20and%20has%20fully%20supported%20Israel%2C%20it%20is%20not%20a%20given%20that%20such%20a%20resolution%20will%20be%20allowed%20to%20pass.%20This%20was%20also%20the%20case%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20v.%20Russia%20case%20because%20Russia%20used%20its%20veto%20to%20prevent%20the%20UN%20security%20council%20from%20actioning%20the%20judgement%20of%20the%20court.%20This%20problem%20of%20enforcement%20may%20explain%20why%20the%20ICJ%20has%20taken%20a%20relatively%20safe%2C%20conservative%20stand%20and%20made%20reference%20to%20the%20obligations%20of%20Hamas%2C%20whom%20it%20has%20no%20jurisdiction%20over.%20Even%20so%2C%20the%20US%20and%20its%20western%20allies%20have%20so%20far%20refused%20to%20criticise%20or%20restrain%20Israel%20in%20any%20manner%20and%20withdrew%20funding%20from%20the%20UN%20Agency%20for%20Palestine%20Refugees%20(UNRWA)%20immediately%20after%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order.%20Despite%20the%20caution%20that%20the%20judges%20have%20shown%2C%20the%20order%20may%20still%20end%20up%20being%20rendered%20ineffective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENonetheless%2C%20this%20order%20may%20cause%20other%20states%20to%20review%20their%20positions%20on%20the%20conflict.%20Encouragement%20from%20its%20supporters%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20order%20may%20persuade%20Israel%20to%20reconsider%20its%20present%20belligerent%20stance%20(the%20government%20referred%20to%20the%20South%20African%20lawyers%20as%20the%20legal%20team%20of%20Hamas).%20For%20instance%2C%20the%20German%20Foreign%20Minister%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fgermany-says-israel-must-adhere-to-icj-ruling-calls-on-hamas-to-free-hostages%2F%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20emphasising%20that%20the%20ICJ%20order%20is%20a%20binding%20legal%20obligation%20on%20Israel.%20How%20the%20court%20responds%20to%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20report%20in%20one%20month%E2%80%99s%20time%20may%20depend%20on%20how%20the%20international%20community%20responds%20to%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20actions%20and%20the%20statements%20of%20its%20officials%20and%20allies%20have%20been%20at%20odds%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20which%20has%20voted%20overwhelmingly%20to%20cease%20the%20conflict%20at%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly.%20The%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20has%20allowed%20both%20sides%20to%20claim%20a%20victory%20and%20may%20ease%20its%20enforcement%20at%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%20Its%20success%20is%20crucial%20for%20thousands%20of%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%20who%20are%20facing%20unimaginable%20conditions%2C%20and%20for%20the%20future%20of%20international%20law%20and%20the%20rules-based%20order%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EUnmekh%20MP%20is%20an%20international%20lawyer%20based%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20with%20a%20specialisation%20in%20matters%20pertaining%20to%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706790589000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F16191217%2FEffect-68.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fin-south-africa-versus-israel-on-gaza-icj-settles-for-a-balancing-act%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Since%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20cannot%20enforce%20its%20orders%2C%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20has%20the%20responsibility%20to%20ensure%20compliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fin-south-africa-versus-israel-on-gaza-icj-settles-for-a-balancing-act%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%