0lack%20of%20big%20ticket%20announcements%20or%20any%20tax%20relief%20in%20the%20interim%20budget%20presented%20by%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20underlined%20the%20ruling%20BJP's%20confidence%20ahead%20of%20the%20national%20election.%20The%20government%20will%20present%20a%20detailed%20roadmap%20to%20pursue%20its%20goal%20of%20Viksit%20Bharat%20in%20its%20full%20budget%20in%20July%2C%20the%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tone%20was%20set%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20yesterday.%20Addressing%20the%20media%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20Budget%20session%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJust%20before%20the%20election%2C%20we%20don't%20submit%20a%20full%20budget%2C%20this%20we%20will%20do%20after%20a%20new%20government%20is%20elected.%20This%20interim%20budget%20is%20a%20guideline%20for%20us.%20I%20am%20hopeful%20that%20the%20country%20will%20touch%20new%20heights%20of%20prosperity.%20Development%20for%20everyone%20is%20taking%20place.%20This%20journey%20will%20continue%20with%20your%20blessings.%20Ram%20Ram.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20this%20is%20not%20a%20full%20budget%2C%20taxpayers%20had%20hoped%20for%20some%20relief%20in%20an%20election%20year.%20There%20was%20buzz%20on%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20government%20revising%20the%20cap%20on%20investment%20exempted%20from%20Income%20Tax.%20Some%20Opposition%20leaders%20had%20also%20expected%20the%20government%20to%20make%20populist%20announcements%20with%20its%20eye%20on%20the%20elections.%20But%20what%20was%20presented%20was%20a%20statement%20of%20confidence%20and%20a%20plan%20to%20keep%20the%20big%20announcements%20for%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20said%20she%20had%20decided%20to%20not%20make%20any%20taxation%20changes%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20convention%20in%20interim%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20welcomed%20the%20budget.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bdraws%20the%20roadmap%26quot%3B%20to%20achieve%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20vision%20of%20a%20Developed%20Bharat%20by%202047.%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20budget%20%26quot%3Bcaptures%20a%20decade%20of%20transformation%2C%20while%20laying%20out%20a%20vision%20of%20further%20development%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekar%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20it%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bexcellent%20summary%20of%20the%20qualitative%20and%20quantitative%20transformation%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%26quot%3B.%20Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20veteran%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20said%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20a%20budget%20to%20speed%20up%20country's%20development%20and%20increase%20employment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%20leaders%20said%20there%20was%20hardly%20anything%20in%20the%20offing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20said%20this%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bfarewell%20budget%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20BJP.%20%26quot%3BA%20budget%20is%20useless%20if%20it%20is%20not%20for%20development%20or%20for%20the%20people.%20The%20BJP%20government%20has%20achieved%20a%20shameful%20record%20by%20completing%20a%20decade%20of%20anti-people%20budgets.%20This%20record%20will%20never%20be%20broken%20because%20the%20time%20of%20a%20progressive%20government%20has%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%20said%20this%20was%20one%20of%20the%20shortest%20Budget%20speeches%20on%20record.%20%26quot%3BNot%20very%20much%20came%20out%20of%20it.%20As%20usual%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20rhetorical%20language%2C%20very%20little%20concrete%20on%20implementation.%20She%20talked%20about%20foreign%20investment%20without%20acknowledging%20that%20that%20investment%20has%20come%20down%20significantly.%20She%20talked%20about%20a%20number%20of%20things%20which%20are%20couched%20in%20vague%20language%20like%20'confidence'%20and%20'hope'%20and%20so%20on.%20But%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20hard%20figures%2C%20very%20few%20figures%20available%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20confidence%20in%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20victory%2C%20reflected%20in%20the%20minister's%20budget%20speech%2C%20is%20not%20without%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20just%20months%20left%20for%20the%20big%20poll%20contest%2C%20the%20Opposition's%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20still%20struggling%20to%20put%20its%20house%20in%20order.%20Seat-sharing%20talks%20have%20hit%20roadblocks%20in%20Bengal%20and%20Punjab.%20In%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20too%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20announced%20some%20candidates%2C%20saying%20that%20it%20does%20not%20require%20Congress's%20clearance.%20In%20Bihar%2C%20the%20exit%20of%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20JDU%20has%20dealt%20a%20big%20blow%20to%20the%20Opposition%20bloc.%20In%20Kerala%2C%20another%20Opposition%20stronghold%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sign%20of%20a%20united%20fight%20either.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706778480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fbobca7jg_budget-nirmala-_625x300_01_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fbudget-2024-nirmala-sitharaman-between-the-lines-bjps-promise-to-come-back-with-full-budget-4972955%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20lack%20of%20big%20ticket%20announcements%20or%20any%20tax%20relief%20in%20the%20interim%20budget%20presented%20by%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20underlined%20the%20ruling%20BJP's%20confidence%20ahead%20of%20the%20national%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fbudget-2024-nirmala-sitharaman-between-the-lines-bjps-promise-to-come-back-with-full-budget-4972955%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fbudget-2024-nirmala-sitharaman-between-the-lines-bjps-promise-to-come-back-