%20Agrawal%20have%20retained%20their%20family%20legacy%20of%20mithai%20making%20with%20Pistabarfi%2C%20a%20cloud%20kitchen%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Harshit%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20is%20Pistabarfi%20the%20new%20Janta%20Dairy%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAbsolutely%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Harshit.%20He%20is%20firm%20that%20the%20former%20was%20created%20as%20an%20ode%20to%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20with%20a%20slightly%20different%20approach.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20end%20consumer%20is%20very%20different%20for%20both%20places.%20Janta%20Dairy%20targets%20the%20locals%20who%20have%20been%20coming%20to%20the%20shop%20since%20my%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20time.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20repeat%20clientele.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Pistabarfi%20has%20a%20niche%20audience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Pistabarfi%20delivers%20all%20over%20India%20and%20is%20well%20on%20its%20way%20to%20coming%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250601%2Faarti-rastogi-bengaluru-food-startup-artinci-healthy-sugar-free-keto-friendly-gluten-free-desserts-ice-cream-brownies-cakes-hearing-disability-woman-entrepreneur-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evalue-added%20snacking%3C%2Fa%3E%20products%20that%20break%20the%20myth%20of%20%3Cem%3Emithais%3C%2Fem%3E%20only%20being%20a%20festive%20reason.%20For%20instance%2C%20take%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekaju%20katli%20mithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20bar%2C%20a%20chocolate%20bar-shaped%20product%20that%20is%20actually%20%3Cem%3Ekaju%20katli%3C%2Fem%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20can%20keep%20it%20in%20their%20pocket%20and%20snack%20on%20it%20when%20they%20want%20to.%20It%20isn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20what%20I%20would%20call%20%E2%80%98fusion%E2%80%99.%20It%E2%80%99s%20more%20like%20we%E2%80%99re%20making%20products%20that%20are%20accessible%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20while%20the