%2C%20at%20events%2C%20and%20through%20their%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CALVE%20is%20derived%20from%20the%20word%20Alveoli%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tiny%20sac-like%20structure%20present%20in%20our%20lungs%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20responsible%20for%20the%20exchange%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20and%20oxygen.%20Without%20this%20organ%2C%20the%20body%20fails%20to%20survive%2C%20thus%20making%20it%20a%20most%20important%20part%20of%20our%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rajiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20he%20explains%20that%20he%20wants%20ALVE%20to%20be%20an%20important%20part%20of%20each%20home%20for%20healthier%20living.%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20create%20products%20that%20not%20only%20meet%20human%20needs%20but%20also%20leave%20a%20positive%20imprint%20on%20our%20planet.%20Our%20vision%20at%20ALVE%20is%20to%20inspire%20a%20world%20where%20fresh%2C%20clean%20air%20is%20not%20a%20luxury%20but%20a%20sustainable%20standard%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706192933000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-24-at-21.41.12-2-1706189293.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339831%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Looking%20for%20ecofriendly%20air%20fresheners%3F%20Jamshedpur's%20Rajiv%20Sharma%20innovated%20ALVE%20smart%20air%20fresheners%20by%20recycling%201500%20kgs%20of%20temple%20flower%20waste.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A29%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339831%2Fjamshedpur-rajiv-sharma-alve-smart-air-fresheners-plastic-free-eco-friendly-temple-flower-waste%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%23GiftaSchoolKit%3A%20This%20Republic%20Day%2C%20Change%20a%20Child%E2%80%99s%20Future%20By%20Donating%20Just%20Rs%20500%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELife%20isn%E